d=\"false\" data-hide=\"false\" contenteditable=\"false\" draggable=\"false\">\n<span data-id=\"43b0ff50574976bb87d512799a168d76\" data-recommend-id=\"image://43b0ff50574976bb87d512799a168d76\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-width=\"3648\" data-height=\"5472\" data-lightbox=\"true\" data-recommended=\"false\" data-hide=\"false\" class=\"js_recommend\"></span></figure>', '2024-01-10 17:47:01', '2024-01-10 17:47:01', 'Our Favorite Cosplay From Katsucon 2022', '', 'cosplay', 'https://kotaku.com/katsucon-2022-cosplay-photos-video-cosplayers-conventio-1848619654', 'Like so much else over the past couple of years, the pandemic hit the cosplay sc...', ''),
(74, NULL, '<img src=\'https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_645/a367ce659c2c5ccc6d83721227bfad0f.jpg\' /><p class=\"sc-77igqf-0 fnnahv\">I’ve lost count of the amount of <em>Neon Genesis Evangelion</em> cosplay I’ve posted on this site over the last 10 years, but pretty much all of it has been focused on the anime’s characters, especially Rei and Asuka. It<!-- -->s enormous mechs are a somewhat trickier proposition.<br></p>\n\n<p class=\"sc-77igqf-0 fnnahv\">A fact that hasn’t stopped Maolo one bit, with this Eva-01 cosplay that’s as remarkable for its finish as it is for <!-- -->its flexibility. While the pic up top (and the one below) look like they’re promo shots for a very expensive action figure, they’re actually a functional suit—complete with lighting—that gives Maolo a full range of movement.</p>\n\n\n<figure class=\"sc-1eow4w5-1 fuSEnv align--bleed js_lazy-image js_marquee-assetfigure\" data-id=\"de961518f551393476ea769b3214448f\" data-recommend-id=\"image://de961518f551393476ea769b3214448f\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-width=\"2048\" data-height=\"1365\" data-lightbox=\"true\" data-recommended=\"false\" data-hide=\"false\" contenteditable=\"false\" draggable=\"false\">\n<span data-id=\"de961518f551393476ea769b3214448f\" data-recommend-id=\"image://de961518f551393476ea769b3214448f\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-width=\"2048\" data-height=\"1365\" data-lightbox=\"true\" data-recommended=\"false\" data-hide=\"false\" class=\"js_recommend\"></span></figure>\n<p class=\"sc-77igqf-0 fnnahv\">The 01 here is Maolo’s third attempt at an <em>Evangelion</em> unit outfit, so they’ve learned a thing or two over the years. It’s<!-- --> the result of a whopping seven months of work.</p>\n\n<p class=\"sc-77igqf-0 fnnahv\">If you’re wondering how the suit can look so crisp while also being so flexible, Maolo has leaned on the classics here for inspiration. Nearly the entire unit is made of pieces of foam that have been individually wrapped in coloured, synthetic leather, which unlike painted pieces can look a lot smoother and metallic.</p>\n\n<p class=\"sc-77igqf-0 fnnahv\">It’s a technique that allows for a suit that both looks and moves well, and is the way shows like <em>Power Rangers </em>(and countless other tokusatsu series) have been made for decades.</p>\n\n<p class=\"sc-77igqf-0 fnnahv\">I’ve mentioned a few times now how the suit moves without actually showing it, so here’s a short video Maolo made that highlights how the suit allows for a surprisingly quick and natural range of movement for something that’s so angular and has so many pieces.</p>\n\n\n<p class=\"sc-77igqf-0 fnnahv\">You can see more of Maolo’s amazing cosplay work <span><a class=\"sc-1out364-0 dPMosf sc-145m8ut-0 erKGZM js_link\" data-ga=\'[[\"Embedded Url\",\"External link\",\"https://twitter.com/SunnyMaolo\",{\"metric25\":1}]]\' href=\"https://twitter.com/SunnyMaolo\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">at their Twitter page</a></span>, including shots of one of their other Evangelion suits, like the one below.</p>\n<figure class=\"sc-1eow4w5-1 fuSEnv align--bleed js_lazy-image js_marquee-assetfigure\" data-id=\"94d9c6140f5146cea8f0901aa06fdff9\" data-recommend-id=\"image://94d9c6140f5146cea8f0901aa06fdff9\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-width=\"2048\" data-height=\"1536\" data-lightbox=\"true\" data-recommended=\"false\" data-hide=\"false\" contenteditable=\"false\" draggable=\"false\">\n<span data-id=\"94d9c6140f5146cea8f0901aa06fdff9\" data-recommend-id=\"image://94d9c6140f5146cea8f0901aa06fdff9\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-width=\"2048\" data-height=\"1536\" data-lightbox=\"true\" data-recommended=\"false\" data-hide=\"false\" class=\"js_recommend\"></span></figure>', '2024-01-10 17:47:01', '2024-01-10 17:47:01', 'Neon Genesis Evangelion Cosplay Gets In The F**king Robot', 'https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_645/a367ce659c2c5ccc6d83721227bfad0f.jpg', 'cosplay', 'https://kotaku.com/neon-genesis-evangelion-cosplay-gets-in-the-fucking-rob-1848134616', 'I’ve lost count of the amount of Neon Genesis Evangelion cosplay I’ve posted on ...', ''),
(75, NULL, '<img src=\'https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_645/c270b6cf72a5688ab1986878a7bd5c4c.jpg\' /><p class=\"sc-77igqf-0 fnnahv\">The return of capacity crowds to English football stadiums has been a beautiful thing to see over the last couple of weeks, but in some cases, fans clearly had a few things to work out of their systems after 18 months stuck watching at home.<br></p>\n\n<p class=\"sc-77igqf-0 fnnahv\">Case in point: the Barnsley v Coventry matchup on the weekend saw a few scuffles ahead of the game, as rival fans clashed on the approach to Barnsley’s home ground Oakwell. It wasn’t anything serious, at least by football violence standards, as fans mostly resorted to just shouting and sticking fingers up at one another, but one notable thing about this little stoush was that a man dressed as Mario got himself arrested.</p>\n\n\n<p class=\"sc-77igqf-0 fnnahv\">As you can see below, amidst all the loud voices a guy dressed as Mario decides to escalate things and start throwing punches, which triggers an immediate police response as he’s hurled to the ground and detained. </p>\n\n<p class=\"sc-77igqf-0 fnnahv\">For what it’s worth, Barnsley won the game 1-0 after Coventry missed a 95th-minute penalty.</p>\n\n\n<figure class=\"sc-1eow4w5-1 fuSEnv align--bleed js_lazy-image js_marquee-assetfigure\" data-id=\"5706c52d4c01ba0df59358fca26ea47b\" data-recommend-id=\"image://5706c52d4c01ba0df59358fca26ea47b\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-width=\"807\" data-height=\"1313\" data-lightbox=\"true\" data-recommended=\"false\" data-hide=\"false\" contenteditable=\"false\" draggable=\"false\">\n<span data-id=\"5706c52d4c01ba0df59358fca26ea47b\" data-recommend-id=\"image://5706c52d4c01ba0df59358fca26ea47b\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-width=\"807\" data-height=\"1313\" data-lightbox=\"true\" data-recommended=\"false\" data-hide=\"false\" class=\"js_recommend\"></span></figure>', '2024-01-10 17:52:01', '2024-01-10 17:52:01', 'Mario Got Himself Arrested Before An English Soccer Game', 'https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_645/c270b6cf72a5688ab1986878a7bd5c4c.jpg', 'cosplay', 'https://kotaku.com/mario-got-himself-arrested-before-an-english-soccer-gam-1847521550', 'The return of capacity crowds to English football stadiums has been a beautiful ...', '');
INSERT INTO `ch_gather` (`id`, `user_id`, `content`, `create_time`, `update_time`, `title`, `image`, `type`, `url`, `introduction`, `column`) VALUES
(76, NULL, '<img src=\'https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_645/d0a9315f42e0d141b040695d08f3a559.jpg\' /><p class=\"sc-77igqf-0 fnnahv\">First shown off in March, Undercover’s new line of <em>Evangelion</em>-inspired outfits are now available for sale. Or should I say,<!-- --> <em>were </em>available for sale, until they almost instantly sold out. We’re now left<!-- --> to either pay apocalyptic resale prices,<!-- --> or, more sensibly, simply look at pictures of them on the internet instead.<br></p>\n\n<p class=\"sc-77igqf-0 fnnahv\">The range features a ton of different pieces, from sweaters to hoodies to shirts, some of them modelled after <em>Evangelion </em>characters, others emblazoned with <em>Evangelion </em>illustrations and logos. </p>\n\n\n<figure class=\"sc-1eow4w5-1 fuSEnv align--bleed js_lazy-image js_marquee-assetfigure\" data-id=\"95bdaee5b8ff02132b1606ef332b6828\" data-recommend-id=\"image://95bdaee5b8ff02132b1606ef332b6828\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-width=\"1565\" data-height=\"1456\" data-lightbox=\"true\" data-recommended=\"false\" data-hide=\"false\" contenteditable=\"false\" draggable=\"false\">\n<span data-id=\"95bdaee5b8ff02132b1606ef332b6828\" data-recommend-id=\"image://95bdaee5b8ff02132b1606ef332b6828\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-width=\"1565\" data-height=\"1456\" data-lightbox=\"true\" data-recommended=\"false\" data-hide=\"false\" class=\"js_recommend\"></span></figure>\n<p class=\"sc-77igqf-0 fnnahv\">Some of the simpler pieces, like the shirts (above, which I quite like), <span><a class=\"sc-1out364-0 dPMosf sc-145m8ut-0 erKGZM js_link\" data-ga=\'[[\"Embedded Url\",\"External link\",\"https://store.undercoverism.com/specialitem/item/detail/1_1_UC2A4881-1_1/Q01\",{\"metric25\":1}]]\' href=\"https://store.undercoverism.com/specialitem/item/detail/1_1_UC2A4881-1_1/Q01\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">could be had for around USD$200 before they sold out</a></span>, which considering we’re talking high-end streetwear in 2021 isn’t <em>too </em>bad. But I’m not here to talk about <em>Evangelion </em>shirts.<br></p>\n\n<p class=\"sc-77igqf-0 fnnahv\">I’m here to talk about the centrepiece of the collection, which is a range of outerwear that goes beyond “inspired by Evangelion” to “Evangelion cosplay.<!-- -->”<!-- --> Like these $5,<!-- -->600 puffer jackets:<br></p>\n\n<figure class=\"sc-1eow4w5-1 fuSEnv align--bleed js_lazy-image js_marquee-assetfigure\" data-id=\"1e0cc9b6f8eb6c329795405cecf49497\" data-recommend-id=\"image://1e0cc9b6f8eb6c329795405cecf49497\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-width=\"2478\" data-height=\"867\" data-lightbox=\"true\" data-recommended=\"false\" data-hide=\"false\" contenteditable=\"false\" draggable=\"false\">\n<span data-id=\"1e0cc9b6f8eb6c329795405cecf49497\" data-recommend-id=\"image://1e0cc9b6f8eb6c329795405cecf49497\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-width=\"2478\" data-height=\"867\" data-lightbox=\"true\" data-recommended=\"false\" data-hide=\"false\" class=\"js_recommend\"></span></figure>\n<p class=\"sc-77igqf-0 fnnahv\">Or these $1,<!-- -->200 turtlenecks,<!-- --> modelled after the kid’s plugsuits:</p>\n<figure class=\"sc-1eow4w5-1 fuSEnv align--bleed js_lazy-image js_marquee-assetfigure\" data-id=\"2cc8fc5a8cadfead0d0a35a24b35f617\" data-recommend-id=\"image://2cc8fc5a8cadfead0d0a35a24b35f617\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-width=\"2490\" data-height=\"889\" data-lightbox=\"true\" data-recommended=\"false\" data-hide=\"false\" contenteditable=\"false\" draggable=\"false\">\n<span data-id=\"2cc8fc5a8cadfead0d0a35a24b35f617\" data-recommend-id=\"image://2cc8fc5a8cadfead0d0a35a24b35f617\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-width=\"2490\" data-height=\"889\" data-lightbox=\"true\" data-recommended=\"false\" data-hide=\"false\" class=\"js_recommend\"></span></figure>\n<p class=\"sc-77igqf-0 fnnahv\">But the real star were these jackets, which with the hoods down look like regular—<!-- -->maybe slightly technical—<!-- -->trench-coats<!-- -->,<!-- -->with  seam taping and practical zips. With hoods up, though, they’re Eva tributes that don’t just model their head designs, but even have remote controls you can use to <em>control the LED eyes</em>.</p>\n<p class=\"sc-77igqf-0 fnnahv\">Here’s an example:</p>\n<figure class=\"sc-1eow4w5-1 fuSEnv align--bleed js_lazy-image js_marquee-assetfigure\" data-id=\"34bb8c73ef24b78436d72c093efd9aba\" data-recommend-id=\"image://34bb8c73ef24b78436d72c093efd9aba\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-width=\"1250\" data-height=\"1558\" data-lightbox=\"true\" data-recommended=\"false\" data-hide=\"false\" contenteditable=\"false\" draggable=\"false\">\n<span data-id=\"34bb8c73ef24b78436d72c093efd9aba\" data-recommend-id=\"image://34bb8c73ef24b78436d72c093efd9aba\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-width=\"1250\" data-height=\"1558\" data-lightbox=\"true\" data-recommended=\"false\" data-hide=\"false\" class=\"js_recommend\"></span></figure>\n<p class=\"sc-77igqf-0 fnnahv\">See? With the hood off, it’s a normal jacket. Zip the hood <em>on</em>, though, and:</p>\n<figure class=\"sc-1eow4w5-1 fuSEnv align--bleed js_lazy-image js_marquee-assetfigure\" data-id=\"c2465e8d2f8ce4b64239417f451bd651\" data-recommend-id=\"image://c2465e8d2f8ce4b64239417f451bd651\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-width=\"1411\" data-height=\"1472\" data-lightbox=\"true\" data-recommended=\"false\" data-hide=\"false\" contenteditable=\"false\" draggable=\"false\">\n<span data-id=\"c2465e8d2f8ce4b64239417f451bd651\" data-recommend-id=\"image://c2465e8d2f8ce4b64239417f451bd651\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-width=\"1411\" data-height=\"1472\" data-lightbox=\"true\" data-recommended=\"false\" data-hide=\"false\" class=\"js_recommend\"></span></figure>\n<p class=\"sc-77igqf-0 fnnahv\">Dim the lights, whip out the branded remote control you get with it, and suddenly:</p>\n<figure class=\"sc-1eow4w5-1 fuSEnv align--bleed js_lazy-image js_marquee-assetfigure\" data-id=\"d315d1e393c2095140cd540d21cf443e\" data-recommend-id=\"image://d315d1e393c2095140cd540d21cf443e\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-width=\"2680\" data-height=\"1538\" data-lightbox=\"true\" data-recommended=\"false\" data-hide=\"false\" contenteditable=\"false\" draggable=\"false\">\n<span data-id=\"d315d1e393c2095140cd540d21cf443e\" data-recommend-id=\"image://d315d1e393c2095140cd540d21cf443e\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-width=\"2680\" data-height=\"1538\" data-lightbox=\"true\" data-recommended=\"false\" data-hide=\"false\" class=\"js_recommend\"></span></figure>\n<p class=\"sc-77igqf-0 fnnahv\">Incredible. There are two more available, each doing the same thing, with the fancy hoods and the light-up eyes.</p>\n<figure class=\"sc-1eow4w5-1 fuSEnv align--bleed js_lazy-image js_marquee-assetfigure\" data-id=\"f4ed1b1713a854ee4758787420f762bd\" data-recommend-id=\"image://f4ed1b1713a854ee4758787420f762bd\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-width=\"2100\" data-height=\"1604\" data-lightbox=\"true\" data-recommended=\"false\" data-hide=\"false\" contenteditable=\"false\" draggable=\"false\">\n<span data-id=\"f4ed1b1713a854ee4758787420f762bd\" data-recommend-id=\"image://f4ed1b1713a854ee4758787420f762bd\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-width=\"2100\" data-height=\"1604\" data-lightbox=\"true\" data-recommended=\"false\" data-hide=\"false\" class=\"js_recommend\"></span></figure>\n<p class=\"sc-77igqf-0 fnnahv\">These last two were the most expensive pieces in the collection, coming in at ¥816,750 each, which works out to be around USD$7,<!-- -->200. Which is absurd, I know, but remember that this isn’t a range designed to be sold in GameStop. It debuted on the catwalk during Tokyo Fashion Week, so adjust your expectations accordingly! </p>', '2024-01-10 17:57:01', '2024-01-10 17:57:01', '$7,000 Evangelion Jackets Are Some Expensive Cosplay', 'https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_645/d0a9315f42e0d141b040695d08f3a559.jpg', 'cosplay', 'https://kotaku.com/7000-evangelion-jackets-are-some-expensive-cosplay-1847926917', 'First shown off in March, Undercover’s new line of Evangelion-inspired outfits a...', ''),
(77, NULL, '<img src=\'\' /><p class=\"sc-77igqf-0 fnnahv\"><strong>WELCOME BACK EVERYONE</strong>. <span><a class=\"sc-1out364-0 dPMosf sc-145m8ut-0 erKGZM js_link\" data-ga=\'[[\"Embedded Url\",\"Internal link\",\"https://kotaku.com/please-enjoy-probably-the-last-cosplay-show-gallery-for-1842952207\",{\"metric25\":1}]]\' href=\"https://kotaku.com/please-enjoy-probably-the-last-cosplay-show-gallery-for-1842952207\">It has been over <em>18 months</em> since we were last able to run a proper cosplay showcase from a major convention</a></span>, but with vaccines and Covid-safe policies in place, Dragon Con 2021 was able to take place in Atlanta last month.</p>\n<p class=\"sc-77igqf-0 fnnahv\">The show spans both the con itself as well as a big parade through the streets of downtown Atlanta. <!-- -->It wasn’t as big as previous years, obviously, with “only” 42,000 people attending—f<!-- -->or context, i<!-- -->n 2019, over <em>80,000</em> people turned up<!-- -->.</p>\n\n<p class=\"sc-77igqf-0 fnnahv\">But that’s still a remarkable figure given the circumstances, and one that in some respects <!-- -->made for a better and more comfortable show for those who <em>did</em> make the trip, since the floors of the convention weren’t as packed as usual. It also gave cosplayers the chance to get creative with their mask use, as you’ll see in quite a few of the shots featured in this gallery.</p>\n<p class=\"sc-77igqf-0 fnnahv\">Below you’ll see some of the cosplay that was on display at Dragon Con 2021, marking the first time most of these folks had got a chance to mingle in public in a costume for well over a year.</p>\n\n<p class=\"sc-77igqf-0 fnnahv\">As usual, <span><a class=\"sc-1out364-0 dPMosf sc-145m8ut-0 erKGZM js_link\" data-ga=\'[[\"Embedded Url\",\"External link\",\"https://www.facebook.com/mineralblu/\",{\"metric25\":1}]]\' href=\"https://www.facebook.com/mineralblu/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">all photos and video are by the talented Mineralblu</a></span>, and you’ll find each cosplayer’s details, including their social media handles and which character they’re cosplaying, watermarked on the image.</p>\n\n\n<figure class=\"sc-1eow4w5-1 fuSEnv align--bleed js_lazy-image js_marquee-assetfigure\" data-id=\"d823046ef97033f10a1c7cf9d620668f\" data-recommend-id=\"image://d823046ef97033f10a1c7cf9d620668f\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-width=\"3648\" data-height=\"5472\" data-lightbox=\"true\" data-recommended=\"false\" data-hide=\"false\" contenteditable=\"false\" draggable=\"false\">\n<span data-id=\"d823046ef97033f10a1c7cf9d620668f\" data-recommend-id=\"image://d823046ef97033f10a1c7cf9d620668f\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-width=\"3648\" data-height=\"5472\" data-lightbox=\"true\" data-recommended=\"false\" data-hide=\"false\" class=\"js_recommend\"></span></figure><figure class=\"sc-1eow4w5-1 fuSEnv align--bleed js_lazy-image js_marquee-assetfigure\" data-id=\"c0caf3a4d38c03ea294f39566c1e81a2\" data-recommend-id=\"image://c0caf3a4d38c03ea294f39566c1e81a2\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-width=\"3648\" data-height=\"5472\" data-lightbox=\"true\" data-recommended=\"false\" data-hide=\"false\" contenteditable=\"false\" draggable=\"false\">\n<span data-id=\"c0caf3a4d38c03ea294f39566c1e81a2\" data-recommend-id=\"image://c0caf3a4d38c03ea294f39566c1e81a2\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-width=\"3648\" data-height=\"5472\" data-lightbox=\"true\" data-recommended=\"false\" data-hide=\"false\" class=\"js_recommend\"></span></figure><figure class=\"sc-1eow4w5-1 fuSEnv align--bleed js_lazy-image js_marquee-assetfigure\" data-id=\"be6af8eaaaf546724935ffc1026aa932\" data-recommend-id=\"image://be6af8eaaaf546724935ffc1026aa932\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-width=\"3648\" data-height=\"5472\" data-lightbox=\"true\" data-recommended=\"false\" data-hide=\"false\" contenteditable=\"false\" draggable=\"false\">\n<span data-id=\"be6af8eaaaf546724935ffc1026aa932\" data-recommend-id=\"image://be6af8eaaaf546724935ffc1026aa932\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-width=\"3648\" data-height=\"5472\" data-lightbox=\"true\" data-recommended=\"false\" data-hide=\"false\" class=\"js_recommend\"></span></figure><figure class=\"sc-1eow4w5-1 fuSEnv align--bleed js_lazy-image js_marquee-assetfigure\" data-id=\"e6596b67b45eba9c1011c70b7fee8517\" data-recommend-id=\"image://e6596b67b45eba9c1011c70b7fee8517\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-width=\"3648\" data-height=\"5472\" data-lightbox=\"true\" data-recommended=\"false\" data-hide=\"false\" contenteditable=\"false\" draggable=\"false\">\n<span data-id=\"e6596b67b45eba9c1011c70b7fee8517\" data-recommend-id=\"image://e6596b67b45eba9c1011c70b7fee8517\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-width=\"3648\" data-height=\"5472\" data-lightbox=\"true\" data-recommended=\"false\" data-hide=\"false\" class=\"js_recommend\"></span></figure>\n<figure class=\"sc-1eow4w5-1 fuSEnv align--bleed js_lazy-image js_marquee-assetfigure\" data-id=\"1d08d5a1edf65597d6e62f69159b50b4\" data-recommend-id=\"image://1d08d5a1edf65597d6e62f69159b50b4\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-width=\"3648\" data-height=\"5472\" data-lightbox=\"true\" data-recommended=\"false\" data-hide=\"false\" contenteditable=\"false\" draggable=\"false\">\n<span data-id=\"1d08d5a1edf65597d6e62f69159b50b4\" data-recommend-id=\"image://1d08d5a1edf65597d6e62f69159b50b4\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-width=\"3648\" data-height=\"5472\" data-lightbox=\"true\" data-recommended=\"false\" data-hide=\"false\" class=\"js_recommend\"></span></figure><figure class=\"sc-1eow4w5-1 fuSEnv align--bleed js_lazy-image js_marquee-assetfigure\" data-id=\"971ab032780c038c62d4f8011a102333\" data-recommend-id=\"image://971ab032780c038c62d4f8011a102333\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-width=\"3648\" data-height=\"5472\" data-lightbox=\"true\" data-recommended=\"false\" data-hide=\"false\" contenteditable=\"false\" draggable=\"false\">\n<span data-id=\"971ab032780c038c62d4f8011a102333\" data-recommend-id=\"image://971ab032780c038c62d4f8011a102333\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-width=\"3648\" data-h