" data-recommended=\"false\" data-hide=\"false\" contenteditable=\"false\" draggable=\"false\">\n<span data-id=\"v9tsmftswiwkadjayqd5\" data-recommend-id=\"image://v9tsmftswiwkadjayqd5\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-width=\"2048\" data-height=\"1366\" data-lightbox=\"true\" data-recommended=\"false\" data-hide=\"false\" class=\"js_recommend\"></span></figure><figure class=\"sc-1eow4w5-1 fuSEnv align--bleed js_lazy-image js_marquee-assetfigure\" data-id=\"xiveh1osumvkpybvknf5\" data-recommend-id=\"image://xiveh1osumvkpybvknf5\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-width=\"2048\" data-height=\"1366\" data-lightbox=\"true\" data-recommended=\"false\" data-hide=\"false\" contenteditable=\"false\" draggable=\"false\">\n<span data-id=\"xiveh1osumvkpybvknf5\" data-recommend-id=\"image://xiveh1osumvkpybvknf5\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-width=\"2048\" data-height=\"1366\" data-lightbox=\"true\" data-recommended=\"false\" data-hide=\"false\" class=\"js_recommend\"></span></figure><figure class=\"sc-1eow4w5-1 fuSEnv align--bleed js_lazy-image js_marquee-assetfigure\" data-id=\"icrklniyfuthl25qqzxz\" data-recommend-id=\"image://icrklniyfuthl25qqzxz\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-width=\"2048\" data-height=\"1366\" data-lightbox=\"true\" data-recommended=\"false\" data-hide=\"false\" contenteditable=\"false\" draggable=\"false\">\n<span data-id=\"icrklniyfuthl25qqzxz\" data-recommend-id=\"image://icrklniyfuthl25qqzxz\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-width=\"2048\" data-height=\"1366\" data-lightbox=\"true\" data-recommended=\"false\" data-hide=\"false\" class=\"js_recommend\"></span></figure><figure class=\"sc-1eow4w5-1 fuSEnv align--bleed js_lazy-image js_marquee-assetfigure\" data-id=\"fzyadioxy1xx4vuenlxz\" data-recommend-id=\"image://fzyadioxy1xx4vuenlxz\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-width=\"1281\" data-height=\"1922\" data-lightbox=\"true\" data-recommended=\"false\" data-hide=\"false\" contenteditable=\"false\" draggable=\"false\">\n<span data-id=\"fzyadioxy1xx4vuenlxz\" data-recommend-id=\"image://fzyadioxy1xx4vuenlxz\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-width=\"1281\" data-height=\"1922\" data-lightbox=\"true\" data-recommended=\"false\" data-hide=\"false\" class=\"js_recommend\"></span></figure>\n<figure class=\"sc-1eow4w5-1 fuSEnv align--bleed js_lazy-image js_marquee-assetfigure\" data-id=\"ac5wpubykgmzd7ezzzcf\" data-recommend-id=\"image://ac5wpubykgmzd7ezzzcf\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-width=\"1303\" data-height=\"1955\" data-lightbox=\"true\" data-recommended=\"false\" data-hide=\"false\" contenteditable=\"false\" draggable=\"false\">\n<span data-id=\"ac5wpubykgmzd7ezzzcf\" data-recommend-id=\"image://ac5wpubykgmzd7ezzzcf\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-width=\"1303\" data-height=\"1955\" data-lightbox=\"true\" data-recommended=\"false\" data-hide=\"false\" class=\"js_recommend\"></span></figure>', '2024-01-10 17:57:01', '2024-01-10 17:57:01', 'Some Of Our Favorite (Pre-Pandemic) Cosplay From 2020', '', 'cosplay', 'https://kotaku.com/some-of-our-favorite-cosplay-from-2020-1846272084', 'While the majority of the year was a complete write-off, for obvious reasons, we...', ''),
(85, NULL, '<img src=\'\' /><p class=\"sc-77igqf-0 fnnahv\">Meet the Violin Samurai. The YouTuber dresses up as iconic characters in ramshackle costumes and then plays video game music. If only he could see half the time!<br></p>\n\n<p class=\"sc-77igqf-0 fnnahv\">In the clip below, for example, he spends the first <!-- -->section <!-- -->trying to get his costume (and the music) right. The actual performance is about three minutes in. It’s terrific. </p>\n\n<p class=\"sc-77igqf-0 fnnahv\">Check out more of his performances as he contends with homemade costumes,<!-- --> and plays beautifully. </p>\n\n\n\n\n<p class=\"sc-77igqf-0 fnnahv\">Not exactly ideal outfits to play in! But we live in less than ideal times. </p>', '2024-01-10 17:57:01', '2024-01-10 17:57:01', 'This Violin-Playing Cosplayer Is The Hero We Need', '', 'cosplay', 'https://kotaku.com/this-violin-playing-cosplayer-is-the-hero-we-need-1846195595', 'Meet the Violin Samurai. The YouTuber dresses up as iconic characters in ramshac...', ''),
(86, NULL, '<img src=\'https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_645/faipvepbuupcsfddwzij.jpg\' /><p class=\"sc-77igqf-0 fnnahv\">It’s fitting that in a year where traditional <!-- --> shoots and shows are going to be off the table, one of our first features is a very lonely, very wonderful<!-- --> collection <!-- -->of <em>Death Stranding</em> cosplay.<br></p>\n\n<aside class=\"sc-1rh3ayr-6 htdlpl inset--story branded-item branded-item--kotaku\" data-commerce-source=\"inset\"><a class=\"sc-1out364-0 dPMosf sc-1rh3ayr-2 bmhLPh inset--story__thumb js_link\" data-ga=\'[[\"Permalink page click\",\"Permalink page click - inset photo\"]]\' href=\"https://kotaku.com/1900-death-stranding-jacket-released-sells-out-instan-1842949514\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">\n<span class=\"sc-ynl58c-0 jbNKBA\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\" aria-label=\"Kotaku avatar\" viewbox=\"0 0 64 64\"><g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\"><path fill=\"#FBC000\" d=\"M0 0h64v64H0z\"></path><path fill=\"#FFF\" d=\"M16.8 49.62l3.67-.14c4.05-.15 7.76-3.2 8.35-6.78l4.13-24.65-10.3-.3-5.84 31.87zM43.19 29.1c3.57.02 4.95 1.29 5.93 3.27l6.84 16.84c-1.73 1.54-9.79 1-12.08-5.04l-2.5-6.72h-1.15c-3.8.06-9.2-2.78-8.03-8.4l11 .05zm-22.2-11.38l-5.59-.16c-7.78-.22-9.93 5.3-9.28 8.88l13.26.13 1.6-8.85zm31.55 7.69c2.62-1.66 3.74-7.65 1.9-9.4l-13.51 3.4c-2.3 1.28-4.94 5.01-2.33 9.15l13.94-3.15z\"></path></g></svg></span></a></aside>\n\n<p class=\"sc-77igqf-0 fnnahv\">The cosplay here is by <span><a class=\"sc-1out364-0 dPMosf sc-145m8ut-0 erKGZM js_link\" data-ga=\'[[\"Embedded Url\",\"External link\",\"https://www.instagram.com/the.mike.knight/?hl=en\",{\"metric25\":1}]]\' href=\"https://www.instagram.com/the.mike.knight/?hl=en\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Mike Knight</a></span>, while the photos are by <span><a class=\"sc-1out364-0 dPMosf sc-145m8ut-0 erKGZM js_link\" data-ga=\'[[\"Embedded Url\",\"External link\",\"https://www.instagram.com/heimeiart/\",{\"metric25\":1}]]\' href=\"https://www.instagram.com/heimeiart/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">heimeiart</a></span>.</p>\n<hr class=\"sc-gcp5ez-1 cvXwRv\">\n<figure class=\"sc-1eow4w5-1 fuSEnv align--bleed js_lazy-image js_marquee-assetfigure\" data-id=\"ctdwqjqbwm7hfww3vryy\" data-recommend-id=\"image://ctdwqjqbwm7hfww3vryy\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-width=\"4000\" data-height=\"6000\" data-lightbox=\"true\" data-recommended=\"false\" data-hide=\"false\" contenteditable=\"false\" draggable=\"false\">\n<span data-id=\"ctdwqjqbwm7hfww3vryy\" data-recommend-id=\"image://ctdwqjqbwm7hfww3vryy\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-width=\"4000\" data-height=\"6000\" data-lightbox=\"true\" data-recommended=\"false\" data-hide=\"false\" class=\"js_recommend\"></span></figure>\n\n<figure class=\"sc-1eow4w5-1 fuSEnv align--bleed js_lazy-image js_marquee-assetfigure\" data-id=\"r5qu5zdip9gfs5i8prqm\" data-recommend-id=\"image://r5qu5zdip9gfs5i8prqm\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-width=\"4000\" data-height=\"6000\" data-lightbox=\"true\" data-recommended=\"false\" data-hide=\"false\" contenteditable=\"false\" draggable=\"false\">\n<span data-id=\"r5qu5zdip9gfs5i8prqm\" data-recommend-id=\"image://r5qu5zdip9gfs5i8prqm\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-width=\"4000\" data-height=\"6000\" data-lightbox=\"true\" data-recommended=\"false\" data-hide=\"false\" class=\"js_recommend\"></span></figure>\n<figure class=\"sc-1eow4w5-1 fuSEnv align--bleed js_lazy-image js_marquee-assetfigure\" data-id=\"p9nhv8ix2n6bsj9h6dtn\" data-recommend-id=\"image://p9nhv8ix2n6bsj9h6dtn\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-width=\"3230\" data-height=\"5194\" data-lightbox=\"true\" data-recommended=\"false\" data-hide=\"false\" contenteditable=\"false\" draggable=\"false\">\n<span data-id=\"p9nhv8ix2n6bsj9h6dtn\" data-recommend-id=\"image://p9nhv8ix2n6bsj9h6dtn\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-width=\"3230\" data-height=\"5194\" data-lightbox=\"true\" data-recommended=\"false\" data-hide=\"false\" cl