recommend-id=\"image://g6zthmbupzpm3ajb318l\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-width=\"4000\" data-height=\"6000\" data-lightbox=\"true\" data-recommended=\"false\" data-hide=\"false\" contenteditable=\"false\" draggable=\"false\">\n<span data-id=\"g6zthmbupzpm3ajb318l\" data-recommend-id=\"image://g6zthmbupzpm3ajb318l\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-width=\"4000\" data-height=\"6000\" data-lightbox=\"true\" data-recommended=\"false\" data-hide=\"false\" class=\"js_recommend\"></span></figure>\n<figure class=\"sc-1eow4w5-1 fuSEnv align--bleed js_lazy-image js_marquee-assetfigure\" data-id=\"dyqon5cp1sr9e7pefyzm\" data-recommend-id=\"image://dyqon5cp1sr9e7pefyzm\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-width=\"4000\" data-height=\"6000\" data-lightbox=\"true\" data-recommended=\"false\" data-hide=\"false\" contenteditable=\"false\" draggable=\"false\">\n<span data-id=\"dyqon5cp1sr9e7pefyzm\" data-recommend-id=\"image://dyqon5cp1sr9e7pefyzm\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-width=\"4000\" data-height=\"6000\" data-lightbox=\"true\" data-recommended=\"false\" data-hide=\"false\" class=\"js_recommend\"></span></figure>', '2024-01-10 17:57:01', '2024-01-10 17:57:01', 'Death Stranding Cosplay Is Very 2021', 'https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_645/faipvepbuupcsfddwzij.jpg', 'cosplay', 'https://kotaku.com/death-stranding-cosplay-is-very-2021-1846194755', 'It’s fitting that in a year where traditional  shoots and shows are going to be ...', ''),
(87, NULL, '<img src=\'https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_645/fekkxlfftvpfrs5cowv2.jpg\' /><p class=\"sc-77igqf-0 fnnahv\">Jarod Nandin, a <em>World of Warcraft </em>player and cosplayer best known for his depiction of <em>South Park’s </em>Jenkins, has died after complications from <!-- -->Covid.<br></p>\n\n<aside class=\"sc-1rh3ayr-6 htdlpl inset--story branded-item branded-item--kotaku\" data-commerce-source=\"inset\"><a class=\"sc-1out364-0 dPMosf sc-1rh3ayr-2 bmhLPh inset--story__thumb js_link\" data-ga=\'[[\"Permalink page click\",\"Permalink page click - inset photo\"]]\' href=\"https://kotaku.com/meet-nwbzpwner-he-has-come-to-judge-you-1465932223\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">\n<span class=\"sc-ynl58c-0 jbNKBA\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\" aria-label=\"Kotaku avatar\" viewbox=\"0 0 64 64\"><g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\"><path fill=\"#FBC000\" d=\"M0 0h64v64H0z\"></path><path fill=\"#FFF\" d=\"M16.8 49.62l3.67-.14c4.05-.15 7.76-3.2 8.35-6.78l4.13-24.65-10.3-.3-5.84 31.87zM43.19 29.1c3.57.02 4.95 1.29 5.93 3.27l6.84 16.84c-1.73 1.54-9.79 1-12.08-5.04l-2.5-6.72h-1.15c-3.8.06-9.2-2.78-8.03-8.4l11 .05zm-22.2-11.38l-5.59-.16c-7.78-.22-9.93 5.3-9.28 8.88l13.26.13 1.6-8.85zm31.55 7.69c2.62-1.66 3.74-7.65 1.9-9.4l-13.51 3.4c-2.3 1.28-4.94 5.01-2.33 9.15l13.94-3.15z\"></path></g></svg></span></a></aside>', '2024-01-10 17:57:01', '2024-01-10 17:57:01', 'Jarod Nandin, \"The South Park Guy\" Cosplayer, Has Died', 'https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_645/fekkxlfftvpfrs5cowv2.jpg', 'cosplay', 'https://kotaku.com/jarod-nandin-the-south-park-guy-cosplayer-has-died-1845987290', 'Jarod Nandin, a World of Warcraft player and cosplayer best known for his depict...', '');
INSERT INTO `ch_gather` (`id`, `user_id`, `content`, `create_time`, `update_time`, `title`, `image`, `type`, `url`, `introduction`, `column`) VALUES
(88, NULL, '<img src=\'\' /><p class=\"sc-77igqf-0 fnnahv\">We were all expecting <span><a class=\"sc-1out364-0 dPMosf sc-145m8ut-0 erKGZM js_link\" data-ga=\'[[\"Embedded Url\",\"Internal link\",\"https://kotaku.com/what-the-fuck-la-comic-con-is-going-ahead-1845208877\",{\"metric25\":1}]]\' href=\"https://kotaku.com/what-the-fuck-la-comic-con-is-going-ahead-1845208877\">most</a></span> 2020 conventions to have been cancelled, but the complete inability of most of the planet—and the United States in particular—to get its shit together means that we’re already starting to see big 2021 shows thrown in the bin as well.<br></p>\n\n<aside class=\"sc-1rh3ayr-6 htdlpl inset--story branded-item branded-item--kotaku\" data-commerce-source=\"inset\"><a class=\"sc-1out364-0 dPMosf sc-1rh3ayr-2 bmhLPh inset--story__thumb js_link\" data-ga=\'[[\"Permalink page click\",\"Permalink page click - inset photo\"]]\' href=\"https://kotaku.com/what-the-fuck-la-comic-con-is-going-ahead-1845208877\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">\n<span class=\"sc-ynl58c-0 jbNKBA\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\" aria-label=\"Kotaku avatar\" viewbox=\"0 0 64 64\"><g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\"><path fill=\"#FBC000\" d=\"M0 0h64v64H0z\"></path><path fill=\"#FFF\" d=\"M16.8 49.62l3.67-.14c4.05-.15 7.76-3.2 8.35-6.78l4.13-24.65-10.3-.3-5.84 31.87zM43.19 29.1c3.57.02 4.95 1.29 5.93 3.27l6.84 16.84c-1.73 1.54-9.79 1-12.08-5.04l-2.5-6.72h-1.15c-3.8.06-9.2-2.78-8.03-8.4l11 .05zm-22.2-11.38l-5.59-.16c-7.78-.22-9.93 5.3-9.28 8.88l13.26.13 1.6-8.85zm31.55 7.69c2.62-1.66 3.74-7.65 1.9-9.4l-13.51 3.4c-2.3 1.28-4.94 5.01-2.33 9.15l13.94-3.15z\"></path></g></svg></span></a></aside>\n\n<p class=\"sc-77igqf-0 fnnahv\">Katsucon is the first, announcing earlier today that “It is with a heavy heart that we must announce the cancellation of Katsucon 2021.”</p>\n\n<p class=\"sc-77igqf-0 fnnahv\">The organiser’s <span><a class=\"sc-1out364-0 dPMosf sc-145m8ut-0 erKGZM js_link\" data-ga=\'[[\"Embedded Url\",\"External link\",\"https://www.katsucon.org/cancellation-details/?fbclid=IwAR1CopbJvG3M430Pi3R40yzCZKrb6DZ5B9bc4I3sfmVjtiKkI2eo9ngLWnQ\",{\"metric25\":1}]]\' href=\"https://www.katsucon.org/cancellation-details/?fbclid=IwAR1CopbJvG3M430Pi3R40yzCZKrb6DZ5B9bc4I3sfmVjtiKkI2eo9ngLWnQ\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">full statement reads</a></span>:</p>\n<blockquote data-type=\"BlockQuote\" class=\"sc-8hxd3p-0 cfcqyq\">\n<p class=\"sc-77igqf-0 fnnahv\">It is with a heavy heart that we must announce the cancellation of Katsucon 2021. This decision was reached after every possible scenario to hold our event safely was considered. We have been working for several months on structural changes to the convention layout and operation in order to make a safe Katsucon 2021 possible. While we had every intention of moving forward with the safest possible convention under these structural changes, in the end, we and the Gaylord National Convention Center have come to the conclusion that we are unable to hold our event up to our standards per current county and state COVID regulations, making it impossible to have Katsucon in February 2021. </p>\n<p class=\"sc-77igqf-0 fnnahv\">While our goal is to put on the best convention possible, ultimately it is the health &amp; safety of our staff, guests, and attendees that is of the utmost concern. We know that this decision may have seemed inevitable in the face of this global pandemic, but that makes this no less heartbreaking to see a Katsucon missed for the first time in 27 years. We at Katsucon, along with the staff from our sister anime conventions throughout the country, join in asking that you stay safe so that we can see you all again in 2022.</p>\n</blockquote>\n\n\n<p class=\"sc-77igqf-0 fnnahv\">Considering we went most of 2020<!-- --> without big shows, the reality that some/most of them won’t be returning until <em>2022 </em>is starting to look like a distinctly depressing reality.</p>\n<aside class=\"sc-1rh3ayr-6 htdlpl inset--story branded-item branded-item--kotaku\" data-commerce-source=\"inset\"><a class=\"sc-1out364-0 dPMosf sc-1rh3ayr-2 bmhLPh inset--story__thumb js_link\" data-ga=\'[[\"Permalink page click\",\"Permalink page click - inset photo\"]]\' href=\"https://kotaku.com/our-favorite-photos-from-katsucon-2020-one-of-the-bigg-1841924139\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">\n<span class=\"sc-ynl58c-0 jbNKBA\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\" aria-label=\"Kotaku avatar\" viewbox=\"0 0 64 64\"><g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\"><path fill=\"#FBC000\" d=\"M0 0h64v64H0z\"></path><path fill=\"#FFF\" d=\"M16.8 49.62l3.67-.14c4.05-.15 7.76-3.2 8.35-6.78l4.13-24.65-10.3-.3-5.84 31.87zM43.19 29.1c3.57.02 4.95 1.29 5.93 3.27l6.84 16.84c-1.73 1.54-9.79 1-12.08-5.04l-2.5-6.72h-1.15c-3.8.06-9.2-2.78-8.03-8.4l11 .05zm-22.2-11.38l-5.59-.16c-7.78-.22-9.93 5.3-9.28 8.88l13.26.13 1.6-8.85zm31.55 7.69c2.62-1.66 3.74-7.65 1.9-9.4l-13.51 3.4c-2.3 1.28-4.94 5.01-2.33 9.15l13.94-3.15z\"></path></g></svg></span></a></aside>', '2024-01-10 17:57:01', '2024-01-10 17:57:01', 'Now 2021 Cosplay Shows Are Being Cancelled As Well', '', 'cosplay', 'https://kotaku.com/now-2021-cosplay-shows-are-being-cancelled-as-well-1845648701', 'We were all expecting most 2020 conventions to have been cancelled, but the comp...', ''),
(89, NULL, '<img src=\'https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_645/gyfurnq4eflkznx92dxa.jpg\' /><p class=\"sc-77igqf-0 fnnahv\">Look, I deeply admire the craft and ingenuity that goes into serious, elaborate cosplay, but I have a very special place in my heart for stuff like this.<br></p>\n\n<p class=\"sc-77igqf-0 fnnahv\">This is<span><a class=\"sc-1out364-0 dPMosf sc-145m8ut-0 erKGZM js_link\" data-ga=\'[[\"Embedded Url\",\"External link\",\"https://www.instagram.com/theladeedanger/\",{\"metric25\":1}]]\' href=\"https://www.instagram.com/theladeedanger/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"> Ladee Danger</a></span>—<span><a class=\"sc-1out364-0 dPMosf sc-145m8ut-0 erKGZM js_link\" data-ga=\'[[\"Embedded Url\",\"Internal link\",\"https://cosplay.kotaku.com/welcome-to-cosplay-kotakus-website-about-cosplay-1739953714\",{\"metric25\":1}]]\' href=\"https://cosplay.kotaku.com/welcome-to-cosplay-kotakus-website-about-cosplay-1739953714\">who you might recognise as Ciri in the banner post for this sub</a></span>—absolutely nailing Halloween as both <em>The Nanny</em> and Peggy from <em>Married with Children</em>.</p>\n\n\n<p class=\"sc-77igqf-0 fnnahv\">Not exactly sights you’ll see often on this cosplay site (or any, for that matter), but then, that’s  why they’re so amazing.</p>', '2024-01-10 17:57:01', '2024-01-10 17:57:01', 'My Heart Is Fully Open For The Nanny &amp; Married With Children Cosplay', 'https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_645/gyfurnq4eflkznx92dxa.jpg', 'cosplay', 'https://kotaku.com/my-heart-is-fully-open-for-the-nanny-married-with-chi-1845554827', 'Look, I deeply admire the craft and ingenuity that goes into serious, elaborate ...', ''),
(90, NULL, '<img src=\'https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_645/gbef2vvhzws0yepgckex.jpg\' /><p class=\"sc-77igqf-0 fnnahv\">Here’s cosplayer <span><a class=\"sc-1out364-0 dPMosf sc-145m8ut-0 erKGZM js_link\" data-ga=\'[[\"Embedded Url\",\"External link\",\"https://www.facebook.com/Knightmage1/\",{\"metric25\":1}]]\' href=\"https://www.facebook.com/Knightmage1/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Knightmage </a></span>with a <em>very</em> good <em>Ghostbusters</em> outfit he made for Halloween.<br></p>\n\n<p class=\"sc-77igqf-0 fnnahv\">The ghost is <span><a class=\"sc-1out364-0 dPMosf sc-145m8ut-0 erKGZM js_link\" data-ga=\'[[\"Embedded Url\",\"External link\",\"https://www.facebook.com/AndiSerpentiCosplay/\",{\"metric25\":1}]]\' href=\"https://www.facebook.com/AndiSerpentiCosplay/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Andi Serpenti</a></span>, while the photographer is <span><a class=\"sc-1out364-0 dPMosf sc-145m8ut-0 erKGZM js_link\" data-ga=\'[[\"Embedded Url\",\"External link\",\"https://www.facebook.com/Blazekphoto/\",{\"metric25\":1}]]\' href=\"https://www.facebook.com/Blazekphoto/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Blazek</a></span>.</p>\n<figure class=\"sc-1eow4w5-1 fuSEnv align--bleed js_lazy-image js_marquee-assetfigure\" data-id=\"y7b43cah6h3uxky0hnhq\" data-recommend-id=\"image://y7b43cah6h3uxky0hnhq\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-width=\"1987\" data-height=\"3000\" data-lightbox=\"true\" data-recommended=\"false\" data-hide=\"false\" contenteditable=\"false\" draggable=\"false\">\n<span data-id=\"y7b43cah6h3uxky0hnhq\" data-recommend-id=\"image://y7b43cah6h3uxky0hnhq\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-width=\"1987\" data-height=\"3000\" data-lightbox=\"true\" data-recommended=\"false\" data-hide=\"false\" class=\"js_recommend\"></span></figure>\n\n<figure class=\"sc-1eow4w5-1 fuSEnv align--bleed js_lazy-image js_marquee-assetfigure\" data-id=\"qnjnqjnjmpko3ozfcbaz\" data-recommend-id=\"image://qnjnqjnjmpko3ozfcbaz\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-width=\"1987\" data-height=\"3000\" data-lightbox=\"true\" data-recommended=\"false\" data-hide=\"false\" contenteditable=\"false\" draggable=\"false\">\n<span data-id=\"qnjnqjnjmpko3ozfcbaz\" data-recommend-id=\"image://qnjnqjnjmpko3ozfcbaz\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-width=\"1987\" data-height=\"3000\" data-lightbox=\"true\" data-recommended=\"false\" data-hide=\"false\" class=\"js_recommend\"></span></figure><figure class=\"sc-1eow4w5-1 fuSEnv align--bleed js_lazy-image js_marquee-assetfigure\" data-id=\"n9ex3ewpygfqyoqxtguj\" data-recommend-id=\"image://n9ex3ewpygfqyoqxtguj\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-width=\"1987\" data-height=\"3000\" data-lightbox=\"true\" data-recommended=\"false\" data-hide=\"false\" contenteditable=\"false\" draggable=\"false\">\n<span data-id=\"n9ex3ewpygfqyoqxtguj\" data-recommend-id=\"image://n9ex3ewpygfqyoqxtguj\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-width=\"1987\" data-height=\"3000\" data-lightbox=\"true\" data-recommended=\"false\" data-hide=\"false\" class=\"js_recommend\"></span></figure>', '2024-01-10 17:57:01', '2024-01-10 17:57:01', 'Fantastic Ghostbusters Cosplay, Dogs And Cats, Living Together', 'https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_645/gbef2vvhzws0yepgckex.jpg', 'cosplay', 'https://kotaku.com/fantastic-ghostbusters-cosplay-dogs-and-cats-living-t-1845544738', 'Here’s cosplayer Knightmage with a very good Ghostbusters outfit he made for Hal...', ''),
(91, NULL, '<img src=\'\' /><p class=\"sc-77igqf-0 fnnahv\">By day, <span><a class=\"sc-1out364-0 dPMosf sc-145m8ut-0 erKGZM js_link\" data-ga=\'[[\"Embedded Url\",\"External link\",\"https://twitter.com/bam1500\",{\"metric25\":1}]]\' href=\"https://twitter.com/bam1500\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Brenden McCormack</a></span> is a developer at Wargaming, working on <em>World of Tanks</em>. In his spare time, though, he’s built (along with his wife Laura) one of the most impressive pieces of Nintendo cosplay I have ever seen.<br></p>\n\n<p class=\"sc-77igqf-0 fnnahv\">In addition to the power-up gif up top, here are<!-- --> a bunch of other photos of the costume in action:</p>\n<figure class=\"sc-1eow4w5-1 fuSEnv align--bleed js_lazy-image js_marquee-assetfigure\" data-id=\"leude1kstpooionq2ium\" data-recommend-id=\"image://leude1kstpooionq2ium\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-width=\"2268\" data-height=\"4032\" data-lightbox=\"true\" data-recommended=\"false\" data-hide=\"false\" contenteditable=\"false\" draggable=\"false\">\n<span data-id=\"leude1kstpooionq2ium\" data-recommend-id=\"image://leude1kstpooionq2ium\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-width=\"2268\" data-height=\"4032\" data-lightbox=\"true\" data-recommended=\"false\" data-hide=\"false\" class=\"js_recommend\"></span></figure>\n\n<figure class=\"sc-1eow4w5-1 fuSEnv align--bleed js_lazy-image js_marquee-assetfigure\" data-id=\"soev9ymgtemohrqkh4qm\" data-recommend-id=\"image://soev9ymgtemohrqkh4qm\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-width=\"2268\" data-height=\"4032\" data-lightbox=\"true\" data-recommended=\"false\" data-hide=\"false\" contenteditable=\"false\" draggable=\"false\">\n<span data-id=\"soev9ymgtemohrqkh4qm\" data-recommend-id=\"image://soev9ymgtemohrqkh4qm\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-width=\"2268\" data-height=\"4032\" data-lightbox=\"true\" data-recommended=\"false\" data-hide=\"false\" class=\"js_recommend\"></span></figure>\n<figure class=\"sc-1eow4w5-1 fuSEnv align--bleed js_lazy-image js_marquee-assetfigure\" data-id=\"agv1dr4dmffhoc2zznes\" data-recommend-id=\"image://agv1dr4dmffhoc2zznes\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-width=\"2268\" data-height=\"4032\" data-lightbox=\"true\" data-recommended=\"false\" data-hide=\"false\" contenteditable=\"false\" draggable=\"false\">\n<span data-id=\"agv1dr4dmffhoc2zznes\" data-recommend-id=\"image://agv1dr4dmffhoc2zznes\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-width=\"2268\" data-height=\"4032\" data-lightbox=\"true\" data-recommended=\"false\" data-hide=\"false\" class=\"js_recommend\"></span></figure>\n<figure class=\"sc-1eow4w5-1 fuSEnv align--bleed js_lazy-image js_marquee-assetfigure\" data-id=\"uzzxu9a163ealdbw9hrj\" data-recommend-id=\"image://uzzxu9a163ealdbw9hrj\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-width=\"2268\" data-height=\"3589\" data-lightbox=\"true\" data-recommended=\"false\" data-hide=\"false\" contenteditable=\"false\" draggable=\"false\">\n<span data-id=\"uzzxu9a163ealdbw9hrj\" data-recommend-id=\"image://uzzxu9a163ealdbw9hrj\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-width=\"2268\" data-height=\"3589\" data-lightbox=\"true\" data-recommended=\"false\" data-hide=\"false\" class=\"js_recommend\"></span></figure>\n<figure class=\"sc-1eow4w5-1 fuSEnv align--bleed js_lazy-image js_marquee-assetfigure\" data-id=\"aa347uox8geyajyw7f7s\" data-recommend-id=\"image://aa347uox8geyajyw7f7s\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-width=\"2268\" data-height=\"4032\" data-lightbox=\"true\" data-recommended=\"false\" data-hide=\"false\" contenteditable=\"false\" draggable=\"false\">\n<span data-id=\"aa347uox8geyajyw7f7s\" data-recommend-id=\"image://aa347uox8geyajyw7f7s\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-width=\"2268\" data-height=\"4032\" data-lightbox=\"true\" data-recommended=\"false\" data-hide=\"false\" class=\"js_recommend\"></span></figure>\n<figure class=\"sc-1eow4w5-1 fuSEnv align--bleed js_lazy-image js_marquee-assetfigure\" data-id=\"yxl6jaxpiiuz8nnvjyha\" data-recommend-id=\"image://yxl6jaxpiiuz8nnvjyha\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-width=\"2268\" data-height=\"4032\" data-lightbox=\"true\" data-recommended=\"false\" data-hide=\"false\" contenteditable=\"false\" draggable=\"false\">\n<span data-id=\"yxl6jaxpiiuz8nnvjyha\" data-recommend-id=\"image://yxl6jaxpiiuz8nnvjyha\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-width=\"2268\" data-height=\"4032\" data-lightbox=\"true\" data-recommended=\"false\" data-hide=\"false\" class=\"js_recommend\"></span></figure>', '2024-01-10 18:02:01', '2024-01-10 18:02:01', 'Metroid Cosplay For The Ages', '', 'cosplay', 'https://kotaku.com/metroid-cosplay-for-the-ages-1845522943', 'By day, Brenden McCormack is a developer at Wargaming, working on World of Tanks...', ''),
(92, NULL, '<img src=\'https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_645/smdmkxppxtl7arpf3gch.jpg\' /><p class=\"sc-77igqf-0 fnnahv\">We’ve seen this before with <span><a class=\"sc-1out364-0 dPMosf sc-145m8ut-0 erKGZM js_link\" data-ga=\'[[\"Embedded Url\",\"Internal link\",\"https://kotaku.com/when-an-overwatch-voice-actor-cosplays-as-her-overwatch-1833251462\",{\"metric25\":1}]]\' href=\"https://kotaku.com/when-an-overwatch-voice-actor-cosplays-as-her-overwatch-1833251462\"><em>Overwatch</em></a></span>, but never with <em>Final Fantasy</em>!<br></p>\n<aside class=\"sc-1rh3ayr-6 htdlpl inset--story branded-item branded-item--kotaku\" data-commerce-source=\"inset\"><a class=\"sc-1out364-0 dPMosf sc-1rh3ayr-2 bmhLPh inset--story__thumb js_link\" data-ga=\'[[\"Permalink page click\",\"Permalink page click - inset photo\"]]\' href=\"https://kotaku.com/when-an-overwatch-voice-actor-cosplays-as-her-overwatch-1833251462\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">\n<span class=\"sc-ynl58c-0 jbNKBA\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\" aria-label=\"Kotaku avatar\" viewbox=\"0 0 64 64\"><g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\"><path fill=\"#FBC000\" d=\"M0 0h64v64H0z\"></path><path fill=\"#FFF\" d=\"M16.8 49.62l3.67-.14c4.05-.15 7.76-3.2 8.35-6.78l4.13-24.65-10.3-.3-5.84 31.87zM43.19 29.1c3.57.02 4.95 1.29 5.93 3.27l6.84 16.84c-1.73 1.54-9.79 1-12.08-5.04l-2.5-6.72h-1.15c-3.8.06-9.2-2.78-8.03-8.4l11 .05zm-22.2-11.38l-5.59-.16c-7.78-.22-9.93 5.3-9.28 8.88l13.26.13 1.6-8.85zm31.55 7.69c2.62-1.66 3.74-7.65 1.9-9.4l-13.51 3.4c-2.3 1.28-4.94 5.01-2.33 9.15l13.94-3.15z\"></path></g></svg></span></a></aside>', '2024-01-10 18:07:01', '2024-01-10 18:07:01', 'Aerith\'s Voice Actor, Cosplaying As Aerith', 'https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_645/smdmkxppxtl7arpf3gch.jpg', 'cosplay', 'https://kotaku.com/aeriths-voice-actor-cosplaying-as-aerith-1845478896', 'We’ve seen this before with Overwatch, but never with Final Fantasy!\n\n...', ''),
(93, NULL, '<img src=\'\' /><p class=\"sc-77igqf-0 fnnahv\">My favourite type of cosplay video isn’t the one where fans are recreating scenes from the show/movie/game they’re cosplaying as. It’s cosplayers doing <span><a class=\"sc-1out364-0 dPMosf sc-145m8ut-0 erKGZM js_link\" data-ga=\'[[\"Embedded Url\",\"Internal link\",\"https://cosplay.kotaku.com/geralt-of-rivia-is-enjoying-his-retirement-1782253768\",{\"metric25\":1}]]\' href=\"https://cosplay.kotaku.com/geralt-of-rivia-is-enjoying-his-retirement-1782253768\">dumb shit like skating as Geralt</a></span>, or recreating the famous “Technoviking” video, only starring the cast of <em>Assassin’s Creed Valhalla</em>.<br></p>\n\n<p class=\"sc-77igqf-0 fnnahv\"><span><a class=\"sc-1out364-0 dPMosf sc-145m8ut-0 erKGZM js_link\" data-ga=\'[[\"Embedded Url\",\"External link\",\"https://www.facebook.com/maulcosplay\",{\"metric25\":1}]]\' href=\"https://www.facebook.com/maulcosplay\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Here’s Maul </a></span>(also star of that Geralt vid) and friends turning medieval England into a German street parade. First, if you need a recap, here’s the original:</p>\n\n<p class=\"sc-77igqf-0 fnnahv\">And now that you’re reacquainted with how it all starts, you can admire just how close Maul sticks to it here:</p>', '2024-01-10 18:07:01', '2024-01-10 18:07:01', 'Techno Viking x Assassin\'s Creed Valhalla', '', 'cosplay', 'https://kotaku.com/technoviking-x-assassins-creed-valhalla-1845478177', 'My favourite type of cosplay video isn’t the one where fans are recreating scene...', ''),
(94, NULL, '<img src=\'https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_645/ygyd3rm7yezxccui1pkn.jpg\' /><p class=\"sc-77igqf-0 fnnahv\">Photographer <span><a class=\"sc-1out364-0 dPMosf sc-145m8ut-0 erKGZM js_link\" data-ga=\'[[\"Embedded Url\",\"External link\",\"https://www.instagram.com/nikolay_photo/\",{\"metric25\":1}]]\' href=\"https://www.instagram.com/nikolay_photo/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Nikolay Zharov</a></span> put this incredible shoot together featuring the work of three cosplayers: <span><a class=\"sc-1out364-0 dPMosf sc-145m8ut-0 erKGZM js_link\" data-ga=\'[[\"Embedded Url\",\"External link\",\"https://www.instagram.com/riddleborn/\",{\"metric25\":1}]]\' href=\"https://www.instagram.com/riddleborn/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Tina Morbid</a></span> (Good Hunter), <span><a class=\"sc-1out364-0 dPMosf sc-145m8ut-0 erKGZM js_link\" data-ga=\'[[\"Embedded Url\",\"External link\",\"https://www.instagram.com/shioncosplay/\",{\"metric25\":1}]]\' href=\"https://www.instagram.com/shioncosplay/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Shion</a></span> (Father Gascoigne) and <span><a class=\"sc-1out364-0 dPMosf sc-145m8ut-0 erKGZM js_link\" data-ga=\'[[\"Embedded Url\",\"External link\",\"https://www.instagram.com/zep_hindle/\",{\"metric25\":1}]]\' href=\"https://www.instagram.com/zep_hindle/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Zep Hindle</a></span> (<!-- -->Old Hunter Henryk).<br></p>\n\n<p class=\"sc-77igqf-0 fnnahv\">The costumes are amazing! Ditto the props! But I also deeply love the action figure-style pedestal shots, it’s a <em>great </em>way to give us a look at a costume in all its glory.</p>\n\n\n<figure class=\"sc-1eow4w5-1 fuSEnv align--bleed js_lazy-image js_marquee-assetfigure\" data-id=\"sjygxt2u1n7hwloddbxh\" data-recommend-id=\"image://sjygxt2u1n7hwloddbxh\" data-format=\"png\" data-width=\"1200\" data-height=\"800\" data-lightbox=\"true\" data-recommended=\"false\" data-hide=\"false\" contenteditable=\"false\" draggable=\"false\">\n<span data-id=\"sjygxt2u1n7hwloddbxh\" data-recommend-id=\"image://sjygxt2u1n7hwloddbxh\" data-format=\"png\" data-width=\"1200\" data-height=\"800\" data-lightbox=\"true\" data-recommended=\"false\" data-hide=\"false\" class=\"js_recommend\"></span></figure>\n<figure class=\"sc-1eow4w5-1 fuSEnv align--bleed js_lazy-image js_marquee-assetfigure\" data-id=\"hbymfdupfxmyhkiq2fvl\" data-recommend-id=\"image://hbymfdupfxmyhkiq2fvl\" data-format=\"png\" data-width=\"1200\" data-height=\"800\" data-lightbox=\"true\" data-recommended=\"false\" data-hide=\"false\" contenteditable=\"false\" draggable=\"false\">\n<span data-id=\"hbymfdupfxmyhkiq2fvl\" data-recommend-id=\"image://hbymfdupfxmyhkiq2fvl\" data-format=\"png\" data-width=\"1200\" data-height=\"800\" data-lightbox=\"true\" data-recommended=\"false\" data-hide=\"false\" class=\"js_recommend\"></span></figure>\n<figure class=\"sc-1eow4w5-1 fuSEnv align--bleed js_lazy-image js_marquee-assetfigure\" data-id=\"ari4p4yke7xkektrlrjl\" data-recommend-id=\"image://ari4p4yke7xkektrlrjl\" data-format=\"png\" data-width=\"1200\" data-height=\"800\" data-lightbox=\"true\" data-recommended=\"false\" data-hide=\"false\" contenteditable=\"false\" draggable=\"false\">\n<span data-id=\"ari4p4yke7xkektrlrjl\" data-recommend-id=\"image://ari4p4yke7xkektrlrjl\" data-format=\"png\" data-width=\"1200\" data-height=\"800\" data-lightbox=\"true\" data-recommended=\"false\" data-hide=\"false\" class=\"js_recommend\"></span></figure>\n<figure class=\"sc-1eow4w5-1 fuSEnv align--bleed js_lazy-image js_marquee-assetfigure\" data-id=\"qc8l4qbsvjjftpj4h5xe\" data-recommend-id=\"image://qc8l4qbsvjjftpj4h5xe\" data-format=\"png\" data-width=\"1200\" data-height=\"800\" data-lightbox=\"true\" data-recommended=\"false\" data-hide=\"false\" contenteditable=\"false\" draggable=\"false\">\n<span data-id=\"qc8l4qbsvjjftpj4h5xe\" data-recommend-id=\"image://qc8l4qbsvjjftpj4h5xe\" data-format=\"png\" data-width=\"1200\" data-height=\"800\" data-lightbox=\"true\" data-recommended=\"false\" data-hide=\"false\" class=\"js_recommend\"></span></figure>\n<figure class=\"sc-1eow4w5-1 fuSEnv align--bleed js_lazy-image js_marquee-assetfigure\" data-id=\"tuhdhywigw6aac7hrqsv\" data-recommend-id=\"image://tuhdhywigw6aac7hrqsv\" data-format=\"png\" data-width=\"1200\" data-height=\"800\" data-lightbox=\"true\" data-recommended=\"false\" data-hide=\"false\" contenteditable=\"false\" draggable=\"false\">\n<span data-id=\"tuhdhywigw6aac7hrqsv\" data-recommend-id=\"image://tuhdhywigw6aac7hrqsv\" data-format=\"png\" data-width=\"1200\" data-height=\"800\" data-lightbox=\"true\" data-recommended=\"false\" data-hide=\"false\" class=\"js_recommend\"></span></figure><figure class=\"sc-1eow4w5-1 fuSEnv align--bleed js_lazy-image js_marquee-assetfigure\" data-id=\"ch95ww8haivrczrqlerh\" data-recommend-id=\"image://ch95ww8haivrczrqlerh\" data-format=\"png\" data-width=\"1200\" data-height=\"800\" data-lightbox=\"true\" data-recommended=\"false\" data-hide=\"false\" contenteditable=\"false\" draggable=\"false\">\n<span data-id=\"ch95ww8haivrczrqlerh\" data-recommend-id=\"image://ch95ww8haivrczrqlerh\" data-format=\"png\" data-width=\"1200\" data-height=\"800\" data-lightbox=\"true\" data-recommended=\"false\" data-hide=\"false\" class=\"js_recommend\"></span></figure>\n<figure class=\"sc-1eow4w5-1 fuSEnv align--bleed js_lazy-image js_marquee-assetfigure\" data-id=\"jgyaoejsqsq5qgu9lpyr\" data-recommend-id=\"image://jgyaoejsqsq5qgu9lpyr\" data-format=\"png\" data-width=\"1200\" data-height=\"800\" data-lightbox=\"true\" data-recommended=\"false\" data-hide=\"false\" contenteditable=\"false\" draggable=\"false\">\n<span data-id=\"jgyaoejsqsq5qgu9lpyr\" data-recommend-id=\"image://jgyaoejsqsq5qgu9lpyr\" data-format=\"png\" data-width=\"1200\" data-height=\"800\" data-lightbox=\"true\" data-recommended=\"false\" data-hide=\"false\" class=\"js_recommend\"></span></figure><figure class=\"sc-1eow4w5-1 fuSEnv align--bleed js_lazy-image js_marquee-assetfigure\" data-id=\"fuofeoucgjohdesbwfra\" data-recommend-id=\"image://fuofeoucgjohdesbwfra\" data-format=\"png\" data-width=\"800\" data-height=\"1200\" data-lightbox=\"true\" data-recommended=\"false\" data-hide=\"false\" contenteditable=\"false\" draggable=\"false\">\n<span data-id=\"fuofeoucgjohdesbwfra\" data-recommend-id=\"image://fuofeoucgjohdesbwfra\" data-format=\"png\" data-width=\"800\" data-height=\"1200\" data-lightbox=\"true\" data-recommended=\"false\" data-hide=\"false\" class=\"js_recommend\"></span></figure>\n<figure class=\"sc-1eow4w5-1 fuSEnv align--bleed js_lazy-image js_marquee-assetfigure\" data-id=\"n5efxacmnmzaydxmvlbf\" data-recommend-id=\"image://n5efxacmnmzaydxmvlbf\" data-format=\"png\" data-width=\"1200\" data-height=\"800\" data-lightbox=\"true\" data-recommended=\"false\" data-hide=\"false\" contenteditable=\"false\" draggable=\"false\">\n<span data-id=\"n5efxacmnmzaydxmvlbf\" data-recommend-id=\"image://n5efxacmnmzaydxmvlbf\" data-format=\"png\" data-width=\"1200\" data-height=\"800\" data-lightbox=\"true\" data-recommended=\"false\" data-hide=\"false\" class=\"js_recommend\"></span></figure>', '2024-01-10 18:07:01', '2024-01-10 18:07:01', 'Bloody Hell Here\'s Some Bloodborne Cosplay', 'https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_645/ygyd3rm7yezxccui1pkn.jpg', 'cosplay', 'https://kotaku.com/bloody-hell-heres-some-bloodborne-cosplay-1845320104', 'Photographer Nikolay Zharov put this incredible shoot together featuring the wor...', ''),
(95, NULL, '<img src=\'https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_645/x76zs6khzza9sjuf7xb6.jpg\' /><p class=\"sc-77igqf-0 fnnahv\">If you’ve got some time coming up, <!-- -->and materials/money to <!-- -->spare<!-- -->, one of the countless ways you could spend all that would be to build your own life-size replica Animal Crossing tools. Because those butterflies aren’t going to catch themselves.<br></p>\n\n<figure class=\"sc-1eow4w5-1 fuSEnv align--bleed js_lazy-image js_marquee-assetfigure\" data-id=\"mhmnttst9ndo7sarhbpz\" data-recommend-id=\"image://mhmnttst9ndo7sarhbpz\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-width=\"1536\" data-height=\"864\" data-lightbox=\"true\" data-recommended=\"false\" data-hide=\"false\" contenteditable=\"false\" draggable=\"false\">\n<span data-id=\"mhmnttst9ndo7sarhbpz\" data-recommend-id=\"image://mhmnttst9ndo7sarhbpz\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-width=\"1536\" data-height=\"864\" data-lightbox=\"true\" data-recommended=\"false\" data-hide=\"false\" class=\"js_recommend\"></span></figure>\n\n<p class=\"sc-77igqf-0 fnnahv\">The wonderful Bill and Britt from Punished Props have put this video together showing how to make both a shovel and a bug net, and if you genuinely want to give it a shot, they’ve got <span><a class=\"sc-1out364-0 dPMosf sc-145m8ut-0 erKGZM js_link\" data-ga=\'[[\"Embedded Url\",\"External link\",\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=sZ37DHS5w20&amp;feature=emb_title\",{\"metric25\":1}]]\' href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=sZ37DHS5w20&amp;feature=emb_title\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">templates available to download in the video’s description</a></span>.<br></p>', '2024-01-10 18:07:01', '2024-01-10 18:07:01', 'Make Your Own Life-Sized Animal Crossing Tools, If You\'re Feeling Crafty', 'https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_645/x76zs6khzza9sjuf7xb6.jpg', 'cosplay', 'https://kotaku.com/make-your-own-life-sized-animal-crossing-tools-if-your-1845281391', 'If you’ve got some time coming up, and materials/money to spare, one of the coun...', ''),
(96, NULL, '<img src=\'https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_645/knqlbvgvckaevg9mxf1u.jpg\' /><p class=\"sc-77igqf-0 fnnahv\"><span><a class=\"sc-1out364-0 dPMosf sc-145m8ut-0 erKGZM js_link\" data-ga=\'[[\"Embedded Url\",\"External link\",\"https://www.facebook.com/lifestreamcos\",{\"metric25\":1}]]\' href=\"https://www.facebook.com/lifestreamcos\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Narga</a></span>, who <span><a class=\"sc-1out364-0 dPMosf sc-145m8ut-0 erKGZM js_link\" data-ga=\'[[\"Embedded Url\",\"Internal link\",\"https://cosplay.kotaku.com/the-queen-of-warcraft-cosplay-1826588911\",{\"metric25\":1}]]\' href=\"https://cosplay.kotaku.com/the-queen-of-warcraft-cosplay-1826588911\">we last saw on this site mastering <em>Warcraft</em> cosplay</a></span>, is now doing the same for <em>The Witcher 3</em>. T<!-- -->his Ciri is <!-- -->just perfect, from the outfit to the scars.<br></p>\n\n<p class=\"sc-77igqf-0 fnnahv\">All photos by <span><a class=\"sc-1out364-0 dPMosf sc-145m8ut-0 erKGZM js_link\" data-ga=\'[[\"Embedded Url\",\"External link\",\"https://www.instagram.com/kmitenkova/?fbclid=IwAR2VWMbwU0IwZzE0_CW3z-shPttvHI8bWpqCptUAinQFs4nhd7oSxEgzaxw\",{\"metric25\":1}]]\' href=\"https://www.instagram.com/kmitenkova/?fbclid=IwAR2VWMbwU0IwZzE0_CW3z-shPttvHI8bWpqCptUAinQFs4nhd7oSxEgzaxw\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">KIRA</a></span> (<span><a class=\"sc-1out364-0 dPMosf sc-145m8ut-0 erKGZM js_link\" data-ga=\'[[\"Embedded Url\",\"Internal link\",\"https://cosplay.kotaku.com/last-of-us-2-cosplay-sure-gets-the-setting-right-1844046033\",{\"metric25\":1}]]\' href=\"https://cosplay.kotaku.com/last-of-us-2-cosplay-sure-gets-the-setting-right-1844046033\">who also took those amazing<em> Last of Us 2</em> shots a few months back</a></span>). And if you’re a cosplayer and want to try something similar, Narga <span><a class=\"sc-1out364-0 dPMosf sc-145m8ut-0 erKGZM js_link\" data-ga=\'[[\"Embedded Url\",\"External link\",\"https://gumroad.com/nargaaoki?fbclid=IwAR1TW0IGQCIfCachJjWxLS-5JLqapu7PcwO_WgaGYDX4e79WqZauuMAnnTs#nUEYr\",{\"metric25\":1}]]\' href=\"https://gumroad.com/nargaaoki?fbclid=IwAR1TW0IGQCIfCachJjWxLS-5JLqapu7PcwO_WgaGYDX4e79WqZauuMAnnTs#nUEYr\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">actually has the outfit’s full how-to guide available for download</a></span>.</p>\n\n\n<hr class=\"sc-gcp5ez-1 cvXwRv\">\n<figure class=\"sc-1eow4w5-1 fuSEnv align--bleed js_lazy-image js_marquee-assetfigure\" data-id=\"fys9vt1bl2ipgl2ct8sa\" data-recommend-id=\"image://fys9vt1bl2ipgl2ct8sa\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-width=\"867\" data-height=\"1300\" data-lightbox=\"true\" data-recommended=\"false\" data-hide=\"false\" contenteditable=\"false\" draggable=\"false\">\n<span data-id=\"fys9vt1bl2ipgl2ct8sa\" data-recommend-id=\"image://fys9vt1bl2ipgl2ct8sa\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-width=\"867\" data-height=\"1300\" data-lightbox=\"true\" data-recommended=\"false\" data-hide=\"false\" class=\"js_recommend\"></span></figure>\n<figure class=\"sc-1eow4w5-1 fuSEnv align--bleed js_lazy-image js_marquee-assetfigure\" data-id=\"oy6k9nvbghyabaoxemsp\" data-recommend-id=\"image://oy6k9nvbghyabaoxemsp\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-width=\"867\" data-height=\"1300\" data-lightbox=\"true\" data-recommended=\"false\" data-hide=\"false\" contenteditable=\"false\" draggable=\"false\">\n<span data-id=\"oy6k9nvbghyabaoxemsp\" data-recommend-id=\"image://oy6k9nvbghyabaoxemsp\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-width=\"867\" data-height=\"1300\" data-lightbox=\"true\" data-recommended=\"false\" data-hide=\"false\" class=\"js_recommend\"></span></figure>\n\n<figure class=\"sc-1eow4w5-1 fuSEnv align--bleed js_lazy-image js_marquee-assetfigure\" data-id=\"s1djcsxyf1khz7fekwu6\" data-recommend-id=\"image://s1djcsxyf1khz7fekwu6\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-width=\"867\" data-height=\"867\" data-lightbox=\"true\" data-recommended=\"false\" data-hide=\"false\" contenteditable=\"false\" draggable=\"false\">\n<span data-id=\"s1djcsxyf1khz7fekwu6\" data-recommend-id=\"image://s1djcsxyf1khz7fekwu6\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-width=\"867\" data-height=\"867\" data-lightbox=\"true\" data-recommended=\"false\" data-hide=\"false\" class=\"js_recommend\"></span></figure><figure class=\"sc-1eow4w5-1 fuSEnv align--bleed js_lazy-image js_marquee-assetfigure\" data-id=\"nir1tecesefp1nwediev\" data-recommend-id=\"image://nir1tecesefp1nwediev\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-width=\"867\" data-height=\"867\" data-lightbox=\"true\" data-recommended=\"false\" data-hide=\"false\" contenteditable=\"false\" draggable=\"false\">\n<span data-id=\"nir1tecesefp1nwediev\" data-recommend-id=\"image://nir1tecesefp1nwediev\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-width=\"867\" data-height=\"867\" data-lightbox=\"true\" data-recommended=\"false\" data-hide=\"false\" class=\"js_recommend\"></span></figure>\n<figure class=\"sc-1eow4w5-1 fuSEnv align--bleed js_lazy-image js_marquee-assetfigure\" data-id=\"zlsm9zo1u6hlmoh3zdhk\" data-recommend-id=\"image://zlsm9zo1u6hlmoh3zdhk\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-width=\"867\" data-height=\"867\" data-lightbox=\"true\" data-recommended=\"false\" data-hide=\"false\" contenteditable=\"false\" draggable=\"false\">\n<span data-id=\"zlsm9zo1u6hlmoh3zdhk\" data-recommend-id=\"image://zlsm9zo1u6hlmoh3zdhk\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-width=\"867\" data-height=\"867\" data-lightbox=\"true\" data-recommended=\"false\" data-hide=\"false\" class=\"js_recommend\"></span></figure>', '2024-01-10 18:07:01', '2024-01-10 18:07:01', 'And Now For Some Incredible Ciri Cosplay', 'https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_645/knqlbvgvckaevg9mxf1u.jpg', 'cosplay', 'https://kotaku.com/and-now-for-some-incredible-ciri-cosplay-1844899897', 'Narga, who we last saw on this site mastering Warcraft cosplay, is now doing the...', ''),
(97, NULL, '<img src=\'https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_645/hu3ptdmj6v6zoehfhv5w.jpg\' /><p class=\"sc-77igqf-0 fnnahv\">It took <span><a class=\"sc-1out364-0 dPMosf sc-145m8ut-0 erKGZM js_link\" data-ga=\'[[\"Embedded Url\",\"External link\",\"https://www.instagram.com/p/CDrGlx4D6fG/\",{\"metric25\":1}]]\' href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/CDrGlx4D6fG/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">amazoniancos </a></span>just a month from first laying eyes on Ubisoft’s design for Eivor earlier in the year <!-- -->to getting this costume together. </p>\n\n<aside class=\"sc-1rh3ayr-6 htdlpl inset--story branded-item branded-item--kotaku\" data-commerce-source=\"inset\"><a class=\"sc-1out364-0 dPMosf sc-1rh3ayr-2 bmhLPh inset--story__thumb js_link\" data-ga=\'[[\"Permalink page click\",\"Permalink page click - inset photo\"]]\' href=\"https://kotaku.com/ubisoft-finally-puts-female-eivor-in-assassin-s-creed-v-1844676085\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">\n<span class=\"sc-ynl58c-0 jbNKBA\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\" aria-label=\"Kotaku avatar\" viewbox=\"0 0 64 64\"><g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\"><path fill=\"#FBC000\" d=\"M0 0h64v64H0z\"></path><path fill=\"#FFF\" d=\"M16.8 49.62l3.67-.14c4.05-.15 7.76-3.2 8.35-6.78l4.13-24.65-10.3-.3-5.84 31.87zM43.19 29.1c3.57.02 4.95 1.29 5.93 3.27l6.84 16.84c-1.73 1.54-9.79 1-12.08-5.04l-2.5-6.72h-1.15c-3.8.06-9.2-2.78-8.03-8.4l11 .05zm-22.2-11.38l-5.59-.16c-7.78-.22-9.93 5.3-9.28 8.88l13.26.13 1.6-8.85zm31.55 7.69c2.62-1.66 3.74-7.65 1.9-9.4l-13.51 3.4c-2.3 1.28-4.94 5.01-2.33 9.15l13.94-3.15z\"></path></g></svg></span></a></aside>', '2024-01-10 18:07:01', '2024-01-10 18:07:01', 'Cosplayers Were Very Ready For Assassin\'s Creed Valhalla', 'https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_645/hu3ptdmj6v6zoehfhv5w.jpg', 'cosplay', 'https://kotaku.com/cosplayers-were-very-ready-for-assassins-creed-valhalla-1844707107', 'It took amazoniancos just a month from first laying eyes on Ubisoft’s design for...', ''),
(98, NULL, '<img src=\'\' /><p class=\"sc-77igqf-0 fnnahv\">Cosplayer Zibartas—<span><a class=\"sc-1out364-0 dPMosf sc-145m8ut-0 erKGZM js_link\" data-ga=\'[[\"Embedded Url\",\"Internal link\",\"https://kotaku.com/oh-boy-look-at-this-doomfist-cosplay-1827988122\",{\"metric25\":1}]]\' href=\"https://kotaku.com/oh-boy-look-at-this-doomfist-cosplay-1827988122\">who we’ve seen here before with some top-tier <em>Overwatch </em>w<!-- -->ork</a></span>—has truly outdone himself here, building a complete set of Mercy’s wings <!-- -->made out of steel and aluminium, that move<!-- --> and <em>really </em>light up.<br></p>\n\n<aside class=\"sc-1rh3ayr-6 htdlpl inset--story branded-item branded-item--kotaku\" data-commerce-source=\"inset\"><a class=\"sc-1out364-0 dPMosf sc-1rh3ayr-2 bmhLPh inset--story__thumb js_link\" data-ga=\'[[\"Permalink page click\",\"Permalink page click - inset photo\"]]\' href=\"https://kotaku.com/oh-boy-look-at-this-doomfist-cosplay-1827988122\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">\n<span class=\"sc-ynl58c-0 jbNKBA\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\" aria-label=\"Kotaku avatar\" viewbox=\"0 0 64 64\"><g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\"><path fill=\"#FBC000\" d=\"M0 0h64v64H0z\"></path><path fill=\"#FFF\" d=\"M16.8 49.62l3.67-.14c4.05-.15 7.76-3.2 8.35-6.78l4.13-24.65-10.3-.3-5.84 31.87zM43.19 29.1c3.57.02 4.95 1.29 5.93 3.27l6.84 16.84c-1.73 1.54-9.79 1-12.08-5.04l-2.5-6.72h-1.15c-3.8.06-9.2-2.78-8.03-8.4l11 .05zm-22.2-11.38l-5.59-.16c-7.78-.22-9.93 5.3-9.28 8.88l13.26.13 1.6-8.85zm31.55 7.69c2.62-1.66 3.74-7.65 1.9-9.4l-13.51 3.4c-2.3 1.28-4.94 5.01-2.33 9.15l13.94-3.15z\"></path></g></svg></span></a></aside>\n\n<p class=\"sc-77igqf-0 fnnahv\">Here’s the finished product:</p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"sc-77igqf-0 fnnahv\">God <em>damn</em>.</p>\n<p class=\"sc-77igqf-0 fnnahv\">If you’d like to see how something like this was put together, Zibartas has made a series of videos breaking down each of the stages of construction, like crafting the metal blades:</p>\n\n<p class=\"sc-77igqf-0 fnnahv\">Getting all the animatronics and engineering in place:</p>\n\n<p class=\"sc-77igqf-0 fnnahv\">And lighting them up:</p>', '2024-01-10 18:07:01', '2024-01-10 18:07:01', 'Overwatch Cosplay Lights Up The Darkness', '', 'cosplay', 'https://kotaku.com/overwatch-cosplay-lights-up-the-darkness-1844599462', 'Cosplayer Zibartas—who we’ve seen here before with some top-tier Overwatch work—...', '');
INSERT INTO `ch_gather` (`id`, `user_id`, `content`, `create_time`, `update_time`, `title`, `image`, `type`, `url`, `introduction`, `column`) VALUES
(99, NULL, '<img src=\'\' /><p class=\"sc-77igqf-0 fnnahv\">With the San Diego Comic-Con cancelled (<span><a class=\"sc-1out364-0 dPMosf sc-145m8ut-0 erKGZM js_link\" data-ga=\'[[\"Embedded Url\",\"External link\",\"https://www.comic-con.org/cci/2020/athome\",{\"metric25\":1}]]\' href=\"https://www.comic-con.org/cci/2020/athome\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">at least in person</a></span>) for 2020, one of the best cosplay events on the planet ended up being cancelled along with it. Bummer. To help remember a time when people <em>could </em>get together in crowds and dress up, then, here’s a retrospective of the last few year’s worth of Comic-Con cosplay showcases.</p>\n<p class=\"sc-77igqf-0 fnnahv\">Our regular cosplay photographer <span><a class=\"sc-1out364-0 dPMosf sc-145m8ut-0 erKGZM js_link\" data-ga=\'[[\"Embedded Url\",\"External link\",\"https://www.facebook.com/mineralblu/\",{\"metric25\":1}]]\' href=\"https://www.facebook.com/mineralblu/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Mineralblu </a></span>put this all together, compiling his favourite video and shots from 2017-onwards. As usual, you’ll find each cosplayer’s social media info, the character they’re cosplaying as and the series it’s from watermarked on each image.</p>\n\n<p class=\"sc-77igqf-0 fnnahv\">Hopefully we’ll able to return in 2021 with a brand new shoot! Maybe. Perhaps.....</p>\n\n\n<figure class=\"sc-1eow4w5-1 fuSEnv align--bleed js_lazy-image js_marquee-assetfigure\" data-id=\"zvztafxihypavf7pywbt\" data-recommend-id=\"image://zvztafxihypavf7pywbt\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-width=\"1365\" data-height=\"2048\" data-lightbox=\"true\" data-recommended=\"false\" data-hide=\"false\" contenteditable=\"false\" draggable=\"false\">\n<span data-id=\"zvztafxihypavf7pywbt\" data-recommend-id=\"image://zvztafxihypavf7pywbt\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-width=\"1365\" data-height=\"2048\" data-lightbox=\"true\" data-recommended=\"false\" data-hide=\"false\" class=\"js_recommen