aku.com/amazon-prime-day-october-big-deal-storage-ps5-switch-pc-1850907400&amp;asc_source=&amp;tag=kinjakotakulink-20\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"sponsored noopener noreferrer nofollow noskim\" data-amazonasin=\"B09X7CFXSX\" data-amazontag=\"kinjakotakulink-20\">here</a></span>\n</li>\n<li>SanDisk 512GB - $28<!-- -->.99 (October 10 &amp; 11) - Buy <span><a class=\"sc-1out364-0 dPMosf sc-145m8ut-0 erKGZM js_link\" data-ga=\"[]\" href=\"https://www.amazon.com/SanDisk-512GB-microSDXC-Memory-Adapter/dp/B0B7NVXLLM?asc_campaign=kinjakotakulink-20&amp;asc_refurl=https://kotaku.com/amazon-prime-day-october-big-deal-storage-ps5-switch-pc-1850907400&amp;asc_source=&amp;tag=kinjakotakulink-20\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"sponsored noopener noreferrer nofollow noskim\" data-amazonasin=\"B0B7NVXLLM\" data-amazontag=\"kinjakotakulink-20\">here</a></span>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"sc-77igqf-0 fnnahv\"><em>*These cards will work on Steam Deck provided you’ve formatted them correctly.</em></p>\n\n<hr class=\"sc-gcp5ez-1 cvXwRv\">\n<p class=\"sc-77igqf-0 fnnahv\">That wraps our selections for storage upgrades. What games are you finally installing once you have the extra space?</p>', '2024-01-10 18:47:01', '2024-01-10 18:47:01', 'The Best October Prime Day Deals On Storage Upgrades For PS5, Xbox, Switch, And PC', 'https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_645/9d5d26faa97649ed1237931b4a97ee98.jpg', 'game-tips', 'https://kotaku.com/amazon-prime-day-october-big-deal-storage-ps5-switch-pc-1850907400', 'Larger install sizes and the diminishing role of physical media in modern games ...', '');
