/yAJFLrftZB6wxGCvbAohTj-480-80.jpg 480w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/yAJFLrftZB6wxGCvbAohTj-650-80.jpg 650w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/yAJFLrftZB6wxGCvbAohTj-970-80.jpg 970w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/yAJFLrftZB6wxGCvbAohTj-1024-80.jpg 1024w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/yAJFLrftZB6wxGCvbAohTj-1200-80.jpg 1200w\" data-sizes=\"(min-width: 1000px) 970px, calc(100vw - 40px)\" data-original-mos=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/yAJFLrftZB6wxGCvbAohTj.jpg\" data-pin-media=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/yAJFLrftZB6wxGCvbAohTj.jpg\"></picture></p>\n<figcaption itemprop=\"caption description\" class=\" inline-layout\"><span class=\"credit\" itemprop=\"copyrightHolder\">(Image credit: Annapurna Interactive)</span></figcaption></figure><p><strong>Release date:</strong> TBC 2024<br><strong>Platform(s):</strong> PC, Xbox Series X/S, PS5&#160;</p>\n<p><u>Ghost Bike</u> is a new adventure from Nidhogg developer, Messhof. Playing as a streetwise kid from Freehub City, you set out to bring back Ghost Bikes, who are said to be magical couriers that rode between the world of the living and the world of the dead. With races along with a variety of different challenges to take on, you can explore what is described as a \"semi open-world\" and discover bike parts to customize your pair of wheels. It looks like one very stylized, intriguing action-adventure with a unique concept at its heart. &#160;</p>\n<h2 id=\"tracks-of-thought\">Tracks of Thought</h2>\n<figure class=\"van-image-figure inline-layout\" data-bordeaux-image-check><p class=\"vanilla-image-block\" style=\"padding-top:56.25%;\"><picture><source type=\"image/webp\" alt=\"Tracks of Thought\" class=\" lazy-image-van\" onerror=\"if(this.src &amp;&amp; this.src.indexOf(\'missing-image.svg\') !== -1){return true;};this.parentNode.replaceChild(window.missingImage(),this)\" data-normal=\"https://vanilla.futurecdn.net/gamesradar/media/img/missing-image.svg\" data-srcset=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurec