\"https://vanilla.futurecdn.net/gamesradar/media/img/missing-image.svg\" data-srcset=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/P9B2BSRaxoVTGKKCE6KPkc-320-80.jpg 320w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/P9B2BSRaxoVTGKKCE6KPkc-480-80.jpg 480w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/P9B2BSRaxoVTGKKCE6KPkc-650-80.jpg 650w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/P9B2BSRaxoVTGKKCE6KPkc-970-80.jpg 970w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/P9B2BSRaxoVTGKKCE6KPkc-1024-80.jpg 1024w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/P9B2BSRaxoVTGKKCE6KPkc-1200-80.jpg 1200w\" data-sizes=\"(min-width: 1000px) 970px, calc(100vw - 40px)\" data-original-mos=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/P9B2BSRaxoVTGKKCE6KPkc.jpg\" data-pin-media=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/P9B2BSRaxoVTGKKCE6KPkc.jpg\"></picture></p>\n<figcaption itemprop=\"caption description\" class=\" inline-layout\"><span class=\"credit\" itemprop=\"copyrightHolder\">(Image credit: Freedom Games)</span></figcaption></figure><p><strong>Release date: </strong>TBC 2024<strong><br>\nPlatform(s): </strong>PC<br><br>Tracks of Thought from developer Tidbits Play sees you take on the role of a lost ladybug aboard a train. Things take a strange turn when the train goes through a mysterious tunnel that causes everyone to forget their final destination. Now, it\'s up to you to find out just what is going on and where the train is headed. By talking to the passengers, make use of Tracks of Thought\'s \"card-based battle-of-wits system\" to resolve conflicts on board. The art style looks absolutely delightful, and it sounds as though we\'ll have a good mystery to delve into. &#160;<br></p>\n<h2 id=\"tiny-glade\">Tiny Glade</h2>\n<figure class=\"van-image-figure inline-layout\" data-bordeaux-image-check><p class=\"vanilla-image-block\" style=\"padding-top:56.25%;\"><picture><source type=\"image/webp\" alt=\"Tiny Glade\" class=\" lazy-image-van\" onerror=\"if(this.src &amp;&amp; this.src.indexOf(\'missing-image.svg\') !== -1){return true;};this.parentNode.replace