src &amp;&amp; this.src.indexOf(\'missing-image.svg\') !== -1){return true;};this.parentNode.replaceChild(window.missingImage(),this)\" data-normal=\"https://vanilla.futurecdn.net/gamesradar/media/img/missing-image.svg\" data-srcset=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/REBrbKRN2PMAhNjTc4yCzW-320-80.jpg 320w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/REBrbKRN2PMAhNjTc4yCzW-480-80.jpg 480w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/REBrbKRN2PMAhNjTc4yCzW-650-80.jpg 650w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/REBrbKRN2PMAhNjTc4yCzW-970-80.jpg 970w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/REBrbKRN2PMAhNjTc4yCzW-1024-80.jpg 1024w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/REBrbKRN2PMAhNjTc4yCzW-1200-80.jpg 1200w\" data-sizes=\"(min-width: 1000px) 970px, calc(100vw - 40px)\" data-original-mos=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/REBrbKRN2PMAhNjTc4yCzW.jpg\" data-pin-media=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/REBrbKRN2PMAhNjTc4yCzW.jpg\"></picture></p>\n<figcaption itemprop=\"caption description\" class=\" inline-layout\"><span class=\"credit\" itemprop=\"copyrightHolder\">(Image credit: Pounce Light)</span></figcaption></figure><p><strong>Release date: </strong>TBC 2024<strong><br>\nPlatform(s): </strong>PC&#160;</p>\n<p>Calling all building fans! If you enjoy creating your own homes or cities, then how about bringing together your very own little castles? Tiny Glade from developer Pounce Light is an upcoming sandbox builder is all about taking everything at your own pace and experimenting to bring to life your own cozy dioramas. Oh, and you can pet sheep - an added bonus.&#160;</p>\n<h2 id=\"afterlove-ep-xa0\">Afterlove EP&#160;</h2>\n<figure class=\"van-image-figure inline-layout\" data-bordeaux-image-check><p class=\"vanilla-image-block\" style=\"padding-top:56.25%;\"><picture><source type=\"image/webp\" alt=\"Afterlove EP\" class=\" lazy-image-van\" onerror=\"if(this.src &amp;&amp; this.src.indexOf(\'missing-image.svg\') !== -1){return true;};this.parentNode.replaceChild(window.missingImage(),this)\" dat