issing-image.svg\') !== -1){return true;};this.parentNode.replaceChild(window.missingImage(),this)\" data-normal=\"https://vanilla.futurecdn.net/gamesradar/media/img/missing-image.svg\" data-srcset=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/A5QUndorYkYR2n7fwB3CeH-320-80.jpg 320w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/A5QUndorYkYR2n7fwB3CeH-480-80.jpg 480w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/A5QUndorYkYR2n7fwB3CeH-650-80.jpg 650w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/A5QUndorYkYR2n7fwB3CeH-970-80.jpg 970w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/A5QUndorYkYR2n7fwB3CeH-1024-80.jpg 1024w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/A5QUndorYkYR2n7fwB3CeH-1200-80.jpg 1200w\" data-sizes=\"(min-width: 1000px) 970px, calc(100vw - 40px)\" data-original-mos=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/A5QUndorYkYR2n7fwB3CeH.jpg\" data-pin-media=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/A5QUndorYkYR2n7fwB3CeH.jpg\"></picture></p>\n<figcaption itemprop=\"caption description\" class=\" inline-layout\"><span class=\"credit\" itemprop=\"copyrightHolder\">(Image credit: Fellow Traveller)</span></figcaption></figure><p><strong>Release date: </strong>TBC 2024<br><strong>Platform(s): </strong>PC, PS4, PS5, Switch</p>\n<p>Afterlove EP is described as a mixture of narrative adventure, dating sim, and rhythm game that will explore an emotional story. Taking place in Jakarta, the capital city of Indonesia, After Love EP follows Rama, a young musician dealing with the loss of their girlfriend Cinta who recently passed away. With beautiful art that\'s brought to life by artist Soyatu and original music from Indonesian band L\'alpahalpha, the upcoming adventure is said to feature multiple possible endings and story paths based on the choices you make.&#160;</p>\n<h2 id=\"duck-detective-the-secret-salami\">Duck Detective: The Secret Salami</h2>\n<figure class=\"van-image-figure inline-layout\" data-bordeaux-image-check><p class=\"vanilla-image-block\" style=\"padding-top:56.25%;\"><picture><source type=\"image/webp\" alt=\"Duck Detectiv