dn.net/2QtoVBbgmgJ3NUzh7Sj8fc.jpg\"></source><img src=\"https://vanilla.futurecdn.net/gamesradar/media/img/missing-image.svg\" alt=\"Duck Detective: The Secret Salami\" class=\" lazy-image-van\" onerror=\"if(this.src &amp;&amp; this.src.indexOf(\'missing-image.svg\') !== -1){return true;};this.parentNode.replaceChild(window.missingImage(),this)\" data-normal=\"https://vanilla.futurecdn.net/gamesradar/media/img/missing-image.svg\" data-srcset=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/2QtoVBbgmgJ3NUzh7Sj8fc-320-80.jpg 320w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/2QtoVBbgmgJ3NUzh7Sj8fc-480-80.jpg 480w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/2QtoVBbgmgJ3NUzh7Sj8fc-650-80.jpg 650w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/2QtoVBbgmgJ3NUzh7Sj8fc-970-80.jpg 970w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/2QtoVBbgmgJ3NUzh7Sj8fc-1024-80.jpg 1024w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/2QtoVBbgmgJ3NUzh7Sj8fc-1200-80.jpg 1200w\" data-sizes=\"(min-width: 1000px) 970px, calc(100vw - 40px)\" data-original-mos=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/2QtoVBbgmgJ3NUzh7Sj8fc.jpg\" data-pin-media=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/2QtoVBbgmgJ3NUzh7Sj8fc.jpg\"></picture></p>\n<figcaption itemprop=\"caption description\" class=\" inline-layout\"><span class=\"credit\" itemprop=\"copyrightHolder\">(Image credit: Happy Broccoli Games)</span></figcaption></figure><p><strong>Release date: </strong>TBC 2024<br><strong>Platform(s): </strong>PC</p>\n<p>Duck Detective: The Secret Salami from developer Happy Broccoli Games is an upcoming gumshoe adventure starring a detective duck with a bread problem, plenty of puns, and some humorous homages to noir detective stories. From investigating to interviewing suspects, you\'ll have to try to fill in the blanks by finding clue words. It\'s described as a mix between Aggretsuko and Obra Dinn, and with a cast of colorful characters to meet and a case to solve, this has wishlist material written all over it.&#160;</p>\n<h2 id=\"paper-trail\">Paper Trail</h2>\n<figure class=\"van-image-figure inline-layout\" data-bordeaux-image-check><p class=\"vanilla-image-block\" style=\"padding-top:56.25%;\"><picture><source type=\"image/webp\" alt=\"Paper Trail\" class=\" lazy-image-van\" onerror=\"if(this.src &amp;&amp; this.src.indexOf(\'missing-image.svg\') !== -1){return true;};this.parentNode.replaceChild(window.missingImage(),this)\" data-normal=\"https://vanilla.futurecdn.net/gamesradar/media/img/missing-image.svg\" data-srcset=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/PQKcqu5QwZoiLeArodcdXJ-320-80.jpg.webp 320w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/PQKcqu5QwZoiLeArodcdXJ-480-80.jpg.webp 480w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/PQKcqu5QwZoiLeArodcdXJ-650-80.jpg.webp 650w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/PQKcqu5QwZoiLeArodcdXJ-970-80.jpg.webp 970w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/PQKcqu5QwZoiLeArodcdXJ-1024-80.jpg.webp 1024w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/PQKcqu5QwZoiLeArodcdXJ-1200-80.jpg.webp 1200w\" data-sizes=\"(min-width: 1000px) 970px, calc(100vw - 40px)\" data-original-mos=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/PQKcqu5QwZoiLeArodcdXJ.jpg\" data-pin-media=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/PQKcqu5QwZoiLeArodcdXJ.jpg\"></source><source type=\"image/jpeg\" alt=\"Paper Trail\" class=\" lazy-image-van\" onerror=\"if(this.src &amp;&amp; this.src.indexOf(\'missing-image.svg\') !== -1){return true;};this.parentNode.replaceChild(window.missingImage(),this)\" data-normal=\"https://vanilla.futurecdn.net/gamesradar/media/img/missing-image.svg\" data-srcset=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/PQKcqu5QwZoiLeArodcdXJ-320-80.jpg 320w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/PQKcqu5QwZoiLeArodcdXJ-480-80.jpg 480w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/PQKcqu5QwZoiLeArodcdXJ-650-80.jpg 650w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/PQKcqu5QwZoiLeArodcdXJ-970-80.jpg 970w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/PQKcqu5QwZoiLeArodcdXJ-1024-80.jpg 1024w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/PQKcqu5QwZoiLeArodcdXJ-1200-80.jpg 1200w\" data-sizes=\"(min-width: 1000px) 970px, calc(100vw - 40px)\" data-original-mos=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/PQKcqu5QwZoiLeArodcdXJ.jpg\" data-pin-media=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/PQKcqu5QwZoiLeArodcdXJ.jpg\"></source><img src=\"https://vanilla.futurecdn.net/gamesradar/media/img/missing-image.svg\" alt=\"Paper Trail\" class=\" lazy-image-van\" onerror=\"if(this.src &amp;&amp; this.src.indexOf(\'missing-image.svg\') !== -1){return true;};this.parentNode.replaceChild(window.missingImage(),this)\" data-normal=\"https://vanilla.futurecdn.net/gamesradar/media/img/missing-image.svg\" data-srcset=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/PQKcqu5QwZoiLeArodcdXJ-320-80.jpg 320w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/PQKcqu5QwZoiLeArodcdXJ-480-80.jpg 480w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/PQKcqu5QwZoiLeArodcdXJ-650-80.jpg 650w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/PQKcqu5QwZoiLeArodcdXJ-970-80.jpg 970w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/PQKcqu5QwZoiLeArodcdXJ-1024-80.jpg 1024w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/PQKcqu5QwZoiLeArodcdXJ-1200-80.jpg 1200w\" data-sizes=\"(min-width: 1000px) 970px, calc(100vw - 40px)\" data-original-mos=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/PQKcqu5QwZoiLeArodcdXJ.jpg\" data-pin-media=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/PQKcqu5QwZoiLeArodcdXJ.jpg\"></picture></p>\n<figcaption itemprop=\"caption description\" class=\" inline-layout\"><span class=\"credit\" itemprop=\"copyrightHolder\">(Image credit: Newfangled Games)</span></figcaption></figure><p><strong>Release date: </strong>TBC 2024<br><strong>Platform(s):</strong> PC, Xbox One, Xbox Series X/S, PS4, PS5&#160;</p>\n<p>Paper Trail looks like a charming new puzzle adventure that takes place in a paper world. Since everything is made of paper, the world itself can fold, rotate, and spin around to allow you to create paths and puzzle your way through locations. Developed by Newfangled Games, Paper Trail is set to explore the story of Paige who\'s just about to leave home for the first time to pursue her studies as an up and coming academic. It certainly has a unique design and concept that has caught our attention, with the added bonus of secrets to uncover.</p>\n<h2 id=\"the-plucky-squire\">The Plucky Squire</h2>\n<figure class=\"van-image-figure inline-layout\" data-bordeaux-image-check><p class=\"vanilla-image-block\" style=\"padding-top:56.25%;\"><picture><source type=\"image/webp\" alt=\"The Plucky Squire\" class=\" lazy-image-van\" onerror=\"if(this.src &amp;&amp; this.src.indexOf(\'missing-image.svg\') !== -1){return true;};this.parentNode.replaceChild(window.missingImage(),this)\" data-normal=\"https://vanilla.futurecdn.net/gamesradar/media/img/missing-image.svg\" data-srcset=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/vKzJLMYe6wMxZ5s9WbXUVW-320-80.jpg.webp 320w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/vKzJLMYe6wMxZ5s9WbXUVW-480-80.jpg.webp 480w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/vKzJLMYe6wMxZ5s9WbXUVW-650-80.jpg.webp 650w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/vKzJLMYe6wMxZ5s9WbXUVW-970-80.jpg.webp 970w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/vKzJLMYe6wMxZ5s9WbXUVW-1024-80.jpg.webp 1024w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/vKzJLMYe6wMxZ5s9WbXUVW-1200-80.jpg.webp 1200w\" data-sizes=\"(min-width: 1000px) 970px, calc(100vw - 40px)\" data-original-mos=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/vKzJLMYe6wMxZ5s9WbXUVW.jpg\" data-pin-media=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/vKzJLMYe6wMxZ5s9WbXUVW.jpg\"></source><source type=\"image/jpeg\" alt=\"The Plucky Squire\" class=\" lazy-image-van\" onerror=\"if(this.src &amp;&amp; this.src.indexOf(\'missing-image.svg\') !== -1){return true;};this.parentNode.replaceChild(window.missingImage(),this)\" data-normal=\"https://vanilla.futurecdn.net/gamesradar/media/img/missing-image.svg\" data-srcset=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/vKzJLMYe6wMxZ5s9WbXUVW-320-80.jpg 320w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/vKzJLMYe6wMxZ5s9WbXUVW-480-80.jpg 480w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/vKzJLMYe6wMxZ5s9WbXUVW-650-80.jpg 650w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/vKzJLMYe6wMxZ5s9WbXUVW-970-80.jpg 970w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/vKzJLMYe6wMxZ5s9WbXUVW-1024-80.jpg 1024w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/vKzJLMYe6wMxZ5s9WbXUVW-1200-80.jpg 1200w\" data-sizes=\"(min-width: 1000px) 970px, calc(100vw - 40px)\" data-original-mos=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/vKzJLMYe6wMxZ5s9WbXUVW.jpg\" data-pin-media=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/vKzJLMYe6wMxZ5s9WbXUVW.jpg\"></source><img src=\"https://vanilla.futurecdn.net/gamesradar/media/img/missing-image.svg\" alt=\"The Plucky Squire\" class=\" lazy-image-van\" onerror=\"if(this.src &amp;&amp; this.src.indexOf(\'missing-image.svg\') !== -1){return true;};this.parentNode.replaceChild(window.missingImage(),this)\" data-normal=\"https://vanilla.futurecdn.net/gamesradar/media/img/missing-image.svg\" data-srcset=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/vKzJLMYe6wMxZ5s9WbXUVW-320-80.jpg 320w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/vKzJLMYe6wMxZ5s9WbXUVW-480-80.jpg 480w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/vKzJLMYe6wMxZ5s9WbXUVW-650-80.jpg 650w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/vKzJLMYe6wMxZ5s9WbXUVW-970-80.jpg 970w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/vKzJLMYe6wMxZ5s9WbXUVW-1024-80.jpg 1024w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/vKzJLMYe6wMxZ5s9WbXUVW-1200-80.jpg 1200w\" data-sizes=\"(min-width: 1000px) 970px, calc(100vw - 40px)\" data-original-mos=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/vKzJLMYe6wMxZ5s9WbXUVW.jpg\" data-pin-media=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/vKzJLMYe6wMxZ5s9WbXUVW.jpg\"></picture></p>\n<figcaption itemprop=\"caption description\" class=\" inline-layout\"><span class=\"credit\" itemprop=\"copyrightHolder\">(Image credit: Devolver Digital)</span></figcaption></figure><p><strong>Release date: </strong>TBC 2024<br><strong>Platform(s): </strong>PC, Xbox Series X/S, PS5, Switch</p>\n<p>The Plucky Squire from developer All Possible Futures <u>looks absolutely magical</u>. With its enchanting concept, The Plucky Squire will see us jump from 2D to 3D as the small but mighty hero Jot, who discovers the world that lies outside of the pages of his storybook home. The debut trailer certainly left a lasting impression, with Toy Story vibes and elements that bring to mind the nostalgic 2D platforming sections of Super Mario Odyssey. After leaving the storybook and emerging into the 3D world of the bedroom, we got to see how Jot can shift between dimensions by jumping onto the surfaces of different objects. It really does look like it has the makings for one creatively charming platforming adventure.</p>\n<h2 id=\"closer-the-distance\">Closer the Distance</h2>\n<figure class=\"van-image-figure inline-layout\" data-bordeaux-image-check><p class=\"vanilla-image-block\" style=\"padding-top:56.25%;\"><picture><source type=\"image/webp\" alt=\"Closer the Distance\" class=\" lazy-image-van\" onerror=\"if(this.src &amp;&amp; this.src.indexOf(\'missing-image.svg\') !== -1){return true;};this.parentNode.replaceChild(window.missingImage(),this)\" data-normal=\"https://vanilla.futurecdn.net/gamesradar/media/img/missing-image.svg\" data-srcset=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/nwVUdBBFQxw9gc4oZPv9y7-320-80.jpg.webp 320w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/nwVUdBBFQxw9gc4oZPv9y7-480-80.jpg.webp 480w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/nwVUdBBFQxw9gc4oZPv9y7-650-80.jpg.webp 650w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/nwVUdBBFQxw9gc4oZPv9y7-970-80.jpg.webp 970w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/nwVUdBBFQxw9gc4oZPv9y7-1024-80.jpg.webp 1024w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/nwVUdBBFQxw9gc4oZPv9y7-1200-80.jpg.webp 1200w\" data-sizes=\"(min-width: 1000px) 970px, calc(100vw - 40px)\" data-original-mos=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/nwVUdBBFQxw9gc4oZPv9y7.jpg\" data-pin-media=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/nwVUdBBFQxw9gc4oZPv9y7.jpg\"></source><source type=\"image/jpeg\" alt=\"Closer the Distance\" class=\" lazy-image-van\" onerror=\"if(this.src &amp;&amp; this.src.indexOf(\'missing-image.svg\') !== -1){return true;};this.parentNode.replaceChild(window.missingImage(),this)\" data-normal=\"https://vanilla.futurecdn.net/gamesradar/media/img/missing-image.svg\" data-srcset=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/nwVUdBBFQxw9gc4oZPv9y7-320-80.jpg 320w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/nwVUdBBFQxw9gc4oZPv9y7-480-80.jpg 480w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/nwVUdBBFQxw9gc4oZPv9y7-650-80.jpg 650w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/nwVUdBBFQxw9gc4oZPv9y7-970-80.jpg 970w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/nwVUdBBFQxw9gc4oZPv9y7-1024-80.jpg 1024w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/nwVUdBBFQxw9gc4oZPv9y7-1200-80.jpg 1200w\" data-sizes=\"(min-width: 1000px) 970px, calc(100vw - 40px)\" data-original-mos=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/nwVUdBBFQxw9gc4oZPv9y7.jpg\" data-pin-media=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/nwVUdBBFQxw9gc4oZPv9y7.jpg\"></source><img src=\"https://vanilla.futurecdn.net/gamesradar/media/img/missing-image.svg\" alt=\"Closer the Distance\" class=\" lazy-image-van\" onerror=\"if(this.src &amp;&amp; this.src.indexOf(\'missing-image.svg\') !== -1){return true;};this.parentNode.replaceChild(window.missingImage(),this)\" data-normal=\"https://vanilla.futurecdn.net/gamesradar/media/img/missing-image.svg\" data-srcset=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/nwVUdBBFQxw9gc4oZPv9y7-320-80.jpg 320w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/nwVUdBBFQxw9gc4oZPv9y7-480-80.jpg 480w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/nwVUdBBFQxw9gc4oZPv9y7-650-80.jpg 650w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/nwVUdBBFQxw9gc4oZPv9y7-970-80.jpg 970w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/nwVUdBBFQxw9gc4oZPv9y7-1024-80.jpg 1024w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/nwVUdBBFQxw9gc4oZPv9y7-1200-80.jpg 1200w\" data-sizes=\"(min-width: 1000px) 970px, calc(100vw - 40px)\" data-original-mos=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/nwVUdBBFQxw9gc4oZPv9y7.jpg\" data-pin-media=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/nwVUdBBFQxw9gc4oZPv9y7.jpg\"></picture></p>\n<figcaption itemprop=\"caption description\" class=\" inline-layout\"><span class=\"credit\" itemprop=\"copyrightHolder\">(Image credit: Skybound Games)</span></figcaption></figure><p><strong>Release date: </strong>TBC 2024<strong><br>\nPlatform(s): </strong>PC, PS5, Xbox Series X/S</p>\n<p>Closer the Distance is a new game from Osmotic Studios that\'s described as a slice of life sim that looks set to us a unique power. As protagonist Angela in the town of Yesterby, you\'ll navigate a story that follows the events after a tragic car accident. With an \"ethereal ability\", Angela can influence the residents of the town, with choices that will be presented that can change the very fate of Yesterby. If you\'re looking for narrative experience with choices that matter, Closer the Distance looks set to be one to keep on eye on.</p>\n<h2 id=\"loco-motive\">Loco Motive</h2>\n<figure class=\"van-image-figure inline-layout\" data-bordeaux-image-check><p class=\"vanilla-image-block\" style=\"padding-top:56.25%;\"><picture><source type=\"image/webp\" alt=\"Loco Motive\" class=\" lazy-image-van\" onerror=\"if(this.src &amp;&amp; this.src.indexOf(\'missing-image.svg\') !== -1){return true;};this.parentNode.replaceChild(window.missingImage(),this)\" data-normal=\"https://vanilla.futurecdn.net/gamesradar/media/img/missing-image.svg\" data-srcset=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/nCHzuaKDE4guMd5YJwjM6W-320-80.jpg.webp 320w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/nCHzuaKDE4guMd5YJwjM6W-480-80.jpg.webp 480w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/nCHzuaKDE4guMd5YJwjM6W-650-80.jpg.webp 650w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/nCHzuaKDE4guMd5YJwjM6W-970-80.jpg.webp 970w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/nCHzuaKDE4guMd5YJwjM6W-1024-80.jpg.webp 1024w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/nCHzuaKDE4guMd5YJwjM6W-1200-80.jpg.webp 1200w\" data-sizes=\"(min-width: 1000px) 970px, calc(100vw - 40px)\" data-original-mos=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/nCHzuaKDE4guMd5YJwjM6W.jpg\" data-pin-media=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/nCHzuaKDE4guMd5YJwjM6W.jpg\"></source><source type=\"image/jpeg\" alt=\"Loco Motive\" class=\" lazy-image-van\" onerror=\"if(this.src &amp;&amp; this.src.indexOf(\'missing-image.svg\') !== -1){return true;};this.parentNode.replaceChild(window.missingImage(),this)\" data-normal=\"https://vanilla.futurecdn.net/gamesradar/media/img/missing-image.svg\" data-srcset=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/nCHzuaKDE4guMd5YJwjM6W-320-80.jpg 320w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/nCHzuaKDE4guMd5YJwjM6W-480-80.jpg 480w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/nCHzuaKDE4guMd5YJwjM6W-650-80.jpg 650w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/nCHzuaKDE4guMd5YJwjM6W-970-80.jpg 970w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/nCHzuaKDE4guMd5YJwjM6W-1024-80.jpg 1024w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/nCHzuaKDE4guMd5YJwjM6W-1200-80.jpg 1200w\" data-sizes=\"(min-width: 1000px) 970px, calc(100vw - 40px)\" data-original-mos=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/nCHzuaKDE4guMd5YJwjM6W.jpg\" data-pin-media=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/nCHzuaKDE4guMd5YJwjM6W.jpg\"></source><img src=\"https://vanilla.futurecdn.net/gamesradar/media/img/missing-image.svg\" alt=\"Loco Motive\" class=\" lazy-image-van\" onerror=\"if(this.src &amp;&amp; this.src.indexOf(\'missing-image.svg\') !== -1){return true;};this.parentNode.replaceChild(window.missingImage(),this)\" data-normal=\"https://vanilla.futurecdn.net/gamesradar/media/img/missing-image.svg\" data-srcset=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/nCHzuaKDE4guMd5YJwjM6W-320-80.jpg 320w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/nCHzuaKDE4guMd5YJwjM6W-480-80.jpg 480w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/nCHzuaKDE4guMd5YJwjM6W-650-80.jpg 650w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/nCHzuaKDE4guMd5YJwjM6W-970-80.jpg 970w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/nCHzuaKDE4guMd5YJwjM6W-1024-80.jpg 1024w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/nCHzuaKDE4guMd5YJwjM6W-1200-80.jpg 1200w\" data-sizes=\"(min-width: 1000px) 970px, calc(100vw - 40px)\" data-original-mos=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/nCHzuaKDE4guMd5YJwjM6W.jpg\" data-pin-media=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/nCHzuaKDE4guMd5YJwjM6W.jpg\"></picture></p>\n<figcaption itemprop=\"caption description\" class=\" inline-layout\"><span class=\"credit\" itemprop=\"copyrightHolder\">(Image credit: Chucklefish)</span></figcaption></figure><p><strong>Release date: </strong>TBC 2024<br><strong>Platform(s): </strong>PC, Switch</p>\n<p>Loco Motive is a pixelated murder mystery from developer Robust Games that takes place onboard an express train in the 1930s. Described as a slapstick comedy adventure with plenty of surprises in store, it sounds as though Loco Motive will take us on quite a ride with point-and-click puzzles, lots of characters to meet, and a crime to investigate as three different protagonists in an interlinking story. &#160;&#160;</p>\n<h3 class=\"article-body__section\" id=\"section-tbc\"><span>TBC</span></h3>\n<h2 id=\"kind-words-2-lofi-city-pop-xa0\">Kind Words 2 (lofi city pop)&#160;</h2>\n<figure class=\"van-image-figure inline-layout\" data-bordeaux-image-check><p class=\"vanilla-image-block\" style=\"padding-top:56.25%;\"><picture><source type=\"image/webp\" alt=\"Kind Words 2\" class=\" lazy-image-van\" onerror=\"if(this.src &amp;&amp; this.src.indexOf(\'missing-image.svg\') !== -1){return true;};this.parentNode.replaceChild(window.missingImage(),this)\" data-normal=\"https://vanilla.futurecdn.net/gamesradar/media/img/missing-image.svg\" data-srcset=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/Ck2KkygGAkF2XcksavoYwf-320-80.jpg.webp 320w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/Ck2KkygGAkF2XcksavoYwf-480-80.jpg.webp 480w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/Ck2KkygGAkF2XcksavoYwf-650-80.jpg.webp 650w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/Ck2KkygGAkF2XcksavoYwf-970-80.jpg.webp 970w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/Ck2KkygGAkF2XcksavoYwf-1024-80.jpg.webp 1024w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/Ck2KkygGAkF2XcksavoYwf-1200-80.jpg.webp 1200w\" data-sizes=\"(min-width: 1000px) 970px, calc(100vw - 40px)\" data-original-mos=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/Ck2KkygGAkF2XcksavoYwf.jpg\" data-pin-media=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/Ck2KkygGAkF2XcksavoYwf.jpg\"></source><source type=\"image/jpeg\" alt=\"Kind Words 2\" class=\" lazy-image-van\" onerror=\"if(this.src &amp;&amp; this.src.indexOf(\'missing-image.svg\') !== -1){return true;};this.parentNode.replaceChild(window.missingImage(),this)\" data-normal=\"https://vanilla.futurecdn.net/gamesradar/media/img/missing-image.svg\" data-srcset=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/Ck2KkygGAkF2XcksavoYwf-320-80.jpg 320w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/Ck2KkygGAkF2XcksavoYwf-480-80.jpg 480w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/Ck2KkygGAkF2XcksavoYwf-650-80.jpg 650w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/Ck2KkygGAkF2XcksavoYwf-970-80.jpg 970w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/Ck2KkygGAkF2XcksavoYwf-1024-80.jpg 1024w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/Ck2KkygGAkF2XcksavoYwf-1200-80.jpg 1200w\" data-sizes=\"(min-width: 1000px) 970px, calc(100vw - 40px)\" data-original-mos=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/Ck2KkygGAkF2XcksavoYwf.jpg\" data-pin-media=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/Ck2KkygGAkF2XcksavoYwf.jpg\"></source><img src=\"https://vanilla.futurecdn.net/gamesradar/media/img/missing-image.svg\" alt=\"Kind Words 2\" class=\" lazy-image-van\" onerror=\"if(this.src &amp;&amp; this.src.indexOf(\'missing-image.svg\') !== -1){return true;};this.parentNode.replaceChild(window.missingImage(),this)\" data-normal=\"https://vanilla.futurecdn.net/gamesradar/media/img/missing-image.svg\" data-srcset=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/Ck2KkygGAkF2XcksavoYwf-320-80.jpg 320w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/Ck2KkygGAkF2XcksavoYwf-480-80.jpg 480w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/Ck2KkygGAkF2XcksavoYwf-650-80.jpg 650w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/Ck2KkygGAkF2XcksavoYwf-970-80.jpg 970w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/Ck2KkygGAkF2XcksavoYwf-1024-80.jpg 1024w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/Ck2KkygGAkF2XcksavoYwf-1200-80.jpg 1200w\" data-sizes=\"(min-width: 1000px) 970px, calc(100vw - 40px)\" data-original-mos=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/Ck2KkygGAkF2XcksavoYwf.jpg\" data-pin-media=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/Ck2KkygGAkF2XcksavoYwf.jpg\"></picture></p>\n<figcaption itemprop=\"caption description\" class=\" inline-layout\"><span class=\"credit\" itemprop=\"copyrightHolder\">(Image credit: Popcannibal)</span></figcaption></figure><p><strong>Release date: </strong>TBC<strong><br>\nPlatform(s): </strong>PC</p>\n<p>Kind Words 2 (lofi city pop) is a followup to 2019\'s Kind Words from developer Popcannibal. As a game that\'s all about being kind to real people, Kind Words saw you writing letters to and from other people, offering words of encouragement, or sharing fears or worries. Now, the second game will carry on the same spirit, with you still being able to write letters from your cozy bedroom, only now you can also venture outside and do a variety of activities - such as writing slam poetry in a cafe, to sharing your wishes from the top of a mountain. It\'s an experience that\'s intended to help you feel seen, heard, and less alone in this busy world of online connection.&#160;</p>\n<h2 id=\"loose-leaf\">Loose Leaf</h2>\n<figure class=\"van-image-figure inline-layout\" data-bordeaux-image-check><p class=\"vanilla-image-block\" style=\"padding-top:56.25%;\"><picture><source type=\"image/webp\" alt=\"Loose Leaf\" class=\" lazy-image-van\" onerror=\"if(this.src &amp;&amp; this.src.indexOf(\'missing-image.svg\') !== -1){return true;};this.parentNode.replaceChild(window.missingImage(),this)\" data-normal=\"https://vanilla.futurecdn.net/gamesradar/media/img/missing-image.svg\" data-srcset=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/pHiFUjkQNABaYE9U7TFa7Z-320-80.jpg.webp 320w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/pHiFUjkQNABaYE9U7TFa7Z-480-80.jpg.webp 480w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/pHiFUjkQNABaYE9U7TFa7Z-650-80.jpg.webp 650w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/pHiFUjkQNABaYE9U7TFa7Z-970-80.jpg.webp 970w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/pHiFUjkQNABaYE9U7TFa7Z-1024-80.jpg.webp 1024w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/pHiFUjkQNABaYE9U7TFa7Z-1200-80.jpg.webp 1200w\" data-sizes=\"(min-width: 1000px) 970px, calc(100vw - 40px)\" data-original-mos=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/pHiFUjkQNABaYE9U7TFa7Z.jpg\" data-pin-media=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/pHiFUjkQNABaYE9U7TFa7Z.jpg\"></source><source type=\"image/jpeg\" alt=\"Loose Leaf\" class=\" lazy-image-van\" onerror=\"if(this.src &amp;&amp; this.src.indexOf(\'missing-image.svg\') !== -1){return true;};this.parentNode.replaceChild(window.missingImage(),this)\" data-normal=\"https://vanilla.futurecdn.net/gamesradar/media/img/missing-image.svg\" data-srcset=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/pHiFUjkQNABaYE9U7TFa7Z-320-80.jpg 320w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/pHiFUjkQNABaYE9U7TFa7Z-480-80.jpg 480w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/pHiFUjkQNABaYE9U7TFa7Z-650-80.jpg 650w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/pHiFUjkQNABaYE9U7TFa7Z-970-80.jpg 970w, https://cdn.mos.c', '2024-03-11 11:51:14', '2024-03-11 11:51:14', 'Upcoming indie games for 2024 and beyond', 'https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/4PaQGwsNXt2oUh3K9kXfwC.jpg', 'games', 'https://www.gamesradar.com/upcoming-indie-games/', 'If you\'re looking for some exciting upcoming indie games to add to your wishlist...', '');
INSERT INTO `ch_gather` (`id`, `user_id`, `content`, `create_time`, `update_time`, `title`, `image`, `type`, `url`, `introduction`, `column`) VALUES
(232, NULL, '<p>A Baldur\'s Gate 3 player who, by their own admission, role-plays \"a klepto monk that practices the Way of the Sticky Hand\" found themselves facing the RPG\'s final gauntlet alone after a spot of petty theft went spectacularly awry.&#160;</p>\n\n<p><strong>Warning: the below contains spoilers for the final part of Baldur\'s Gate 3, so if you\'re still on your first playthrough, you might want to look away now.</strong></p>\n<p>The player, who goes by Saquon, recounted their unfortunate tale over on the Baldur\'s Gate 3 subreddit. Having made a rousing speech to their companions, the player set about making their final preparations before the big end battle. This included a spot of trading with a merchant whereby a sword caught their eye.&#160;</p>\n\n\n<p>\"I saw he had a sword on his table, so I gave it a yoink, thinking I was hidden,\" Saquon explains. \"Immediately, all my allies in the room disappear, and just the flaming fist guy is left, who immediately moves to attack me. Doesn\'t even give me a chance to explain if it\'s a misunderstanding.\"</p>\n\n<p>Having killed the assailant in self-defense, the player continues towards the final task, taking out the Netherbrain. Between them and it are numerous formidable foes, including a great big dragon. About to take on the fire-breathing beast, the player suddenly realizes they\'re all alone. \"They actually abandoned me and the fate of The Realms over one little sword,\" Saquon says. \"After all we\'d been through.\"</p>\n\n<p>To the player, throwing the towel in over a single stolen piece of equipment \"seems kind of petty,\" and they\'re not the only one who has accidentally ruined their playthrough right at the end in this way. \"Happened to me too, I was left speechless,\" says DeadTemplar. \"Like, why did you even put that thing on the table if it\'s not for the taking!?\" Even worse, another player says they didn\'t see the sword in question and \"clicked it by accident.\"</p>\n<p>According to some in the comments, this increased hostility towards stealing came about after the arrival of Patch 6, which Larian rolled out last month. One player in the comments says that before the patch was implemented, they did the same thing with \"no consequences,\" as they were simply told that they had to pay for the sword when they tried to steal it. Another says that previously, when attempting to pilfer a potion, the merchant would offer to sell it to them, but following Patch 6, \"all of them aggro the moment I steal it.\"</p>\n<p>So let that be a lesson to all of us to think twice before bolstering our inventories using the five-finger discount, particularly in Baldur\'s Gate 3\'s Honour Mode, where our transgressions can\'t be undone by a simple reload.</p>\n<p><em>Our own Ali Jones, thankfully with companions in tow, managed to </em><em>beat Baldur\'s Gate 3\'s final gauntlet with a whole new fighting style and a healthy dose of RNG</em><em>.</em></p>', '2024-03-11 11:51:14', '2024-03-11 11:51:14', 'Baldur\'s Gate 3 Monk \"that practices the Way of the Sticky Hand\" forced to do the final fight alone after angering most of the RPG\'s cast by stealing one sword', 'https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/mNKVrHQwhXzF4FRpfRGLQg.jpg', 'games', 'https://www.gamesradar.com/baldurs-gate-3-monk-that-practices-the-way-of-the-sticky-hand-forced-to-do-the-final-fight-alone-after-angering-most-of-the-rpgs-cast-by-stealing-one-sword/', 'A Baldur\'s Gate 3 player who, by their own admission, role-plays \"a klepto monk ...', ''),
(233, NULL, '<p>There are so many upcoming Assassin\'s Creed games in the works. From an interesting project that\'s coming in the form of an interactive hub, to the next flagship, open-world adventure, there\'s plenty in the pipeline to keep track of and look out when it comes to Ubisoft\'s long-running stealth series from Ubisoft.&#160;</p>\n\n<p>After Assassin\'s Creed Mirage delivered a smaller-scale experience following the story of Basim before the events of Assassin\'s Creed Valhalla, we\'re set to see a bigger adventure that will take us Japan, along with some exciting new entries we can\'t wait to learn more about. Alongside a lineup of upcoming Ubisoft games and new games for 2024, there\'s a lot to watch out for in the future.&#160;</p>\n<p>For a recap of all of the upcoming Assassin\'s Creed games coming our way, read on below.&#160;</p>\n\n\n\n\n<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewbox=\"0 0 20 20\" width=\"16.67\" height=\"16.67\"><path d=\"M3 3 1.5 1.5a1 1 0 0 0-1.6.7v4.3c0 .5.4.9 1 .9h4.2A1 1 0 0 0 6 5.9L4.7 4.7A7.5 7.5 0 0 1 17.5 10a7.5 7.5 0 0 1-11.8 6.2 1.3 1.3 0 0 0-1.4 2A10 10 0 1 0 2.9 3Zm7 2a1 1 0 0 0-1 1v4c0 .3.2.5.3.7l2.8 2.8c.4.3 1 .3 1.4 0 .3-.4.3-1 0-1.3l-2.6-2.6V6c0-.5-.4-.9-.9-.9Z\"></path></svg><h5 class=\"info-block__layout-title\">Recent updates</h5>\n\n<p class=\"infoUpdate-log\">This roundup of upcoming Assassin\'s Creed games was updated on March 8 to ensure everything is as up to date as possible.&#160;</p>\n\n<h3 class=\"article-body__section\" id=\"section-upcoming-assassin-s-creed-games\"><span>Upcoming Assassin\'s Creed games</span></h3>\n<h2 id=\"assassin-apos-s-creed-infinity\">Assassin\'s Creed Infinity</h2>\n<figure class=\"van-image-figure inline-layout\" data-bordeaux-image-check><p class=\"vanilla-image-block\" style=\"padding-top:56.25%;\"><picture><source type=\"image/webp\" alt=\"Assassin\'s Creed Infinity\" class=\" lazy-image-van\" onerror=\"if(this.src &amp;&amp; this.src.indexOf(\'missing-image.svg\') !== -1){return true;};this.parentNode.replaceChild(window.missingImage(),this)\" data-normal=\"https://vanilla.futurecdn.net/gamesradar/media/img/missing-image.svg\" data-srcset=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/dbS6M6ZVjqXnY35JFrnA2G-320-80.jpg.webp 320w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/dbS6M6ZVjqXnY35JFrnA2G-480-80.jpg.webp 480w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/dbS6M6ZVjqXnY35JFrnA2G-650-80.jpg.webp 650w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/dbS6M6ZVjqXnY35JFrnA2G-970-80.jpg.webp 970w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/dbS6M6ZVjqXnY35JFrnA2G-1024-80.jpg.webp 1024w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/dbS6M6ZVjqXnY35JFrnA2G-1200-80.jpg.webp 1200w\" data-sizes=\"(min-width: 1000px) 970px, calc(100vw - 40px)\" data-original-mos=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/dbS6M6ZVjqXnY35JFrnA2G.jpg\" data-pin-media=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/dbS6M6ZVjqXnY35JFrnA2G.jpg\"></source><source type=\"image/jpeg\" alt=\"Assassin\'s Creed Infinity\" class=\" lazy-image-van\" onerror=\"if(this.src &amp;&amp; this.src.indexOf(\'missing-image.svg\') !== -1){return true;};this.parentNode.replaceChild(window.missingImage(),this)\" data-normal=\"https://vanilla.futurecdn.net/gamesradar/media/img/missing-image.svg\" data-srcset=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/dbS6M6ZVjqXnY35JFrnA2G-320-80.jpg 320w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/dbS6M6ZVjqXnY35JFrnA2G-480-80.jpg 480w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/dbS6M6ZVjqXnY35JFrnA2G-650-80.jpg 650w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/dbS6M6ZVjqXnY35JFrnA2G-970-80.jpg 970w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/dbS6M6ZVjqXnY35JFrnA2G-1024-80.jpg 1024w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/dbS6M6ZVjqXnY35JFrnA2G-1200-80.jpg 1200w\" data-sizes=\"(min-width: 1000px) 970px, calc(100vw - 40px)\" data-original-mos=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/dbS6M6ZVjqXnY35JFrnA2G.jpg\" data-pin-media=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/dbS6M6ZVjqXnY35JFrnA2G.jpg\"></source><img src=\"https://vanilla.futurecdn.net/gamesradar/media/img/missing-image.svg\" alt=\"Assassin\'s Creed Infinity\" class=\" lazy-image-van\" onerror=\"if(this.src &amp;&amp; this.src.indexOf(\'missing-image.svg\') !== -1){return true;};this.parentNode.replaceChild(window.missingImage(),this)\" data-normal=\"https://vanilla.futurecdn.net/gamesradar/media/img/missing-image.svg\" data-srcset=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/dbS6M6ZVjqXnY35JFrnA2G-320-80.jpg 320w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/dbS6M6ZVjqXnY35JFrnA2G-480-80.jpg 480w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/dbS6M6ZVjqXnY35JFrnA2G-650-80.jpg 650w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/dbS6M6ZVjqXnY35JFrnA2G-970-80.jpg 970w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/dbS6M6ZVjqXnY35JFrnA2G-1024-80.jpg 1024w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/dbS6M6ZVjqXnY35JFrnA2G-1200-80.jpg 1200w\" data-sizes=\"(min-width: 1000px) 970px, calc(100vw - 40px)\" data-original-mos=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/dbS6M6ZVjqXnY35JFrnA2G.jpg\" data-pin-media=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/dbS6M6ZVjqXnY35JFrnA2G.jpg\"></picture></p>\n<figcaption itemprop=\"caption description\" class=\" inline-layout\"><span class=\"credit\" itemprop=\"copyrightHolder\">(Image credit: Ubisoft)</span></figcaption></figure><p><strong>Developer: </strong>Ubisoft Quebec, Ubisoft Montreal&#160;<br><strong>Platform(s):</strong> TBC<br><strong>Release date:</strong> TBC</p>\n\n<p>Assassin\'s Creed Infinity is difficult to explain, but it could have a transformative impact on the way that we interact with Assassin\'s Creed games in the future. Ubisoft is effectively building an interactive hub that will function like the Animus, allowing you to jump between different historical playgrounds while simultaneously progressing the modern-day narrative framing that has been with the series since the beginning. The first two games to join the Infinity Hub will be Assassin\'s Creed Codename Red and Assassin\'s Creed Codename Hexe, and it is then expected to expand and evolve over time. It\'s a little metaverse-y, but it also makes perfect sense for this franchise.&#160;</p>\n\n<h2 id=\"assassin-apos-s-creed-codename-red\">Assassin\'s Creed Codename Red</h2>\n<figure class=\"van-image-figure inline-layout\" data-bordeaux-image-check><p class=\"vanilla-image-block\" style=\"padding-top:56.25%;\"><picture><source type=\"image/webp\" alt=\"Assassin\'s Creed Codename Red\" class=\" lazy-image-van\" onerror=\"if(this.src &amp;&amp; this.src.indexOf(\'missing-image.svg\') !== -1){return true;};this.parentNode.replaceChild(window.missingImage(),this)\" data-normal=\"https://vanilla.futurecdn.net/gamesradar/media/img/missing-image.svg\" data-srcset=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/2qAsGfTHizMsQMUD5h6teB-320-80.jpg.webp 320w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/2qAsGfTHizMsQMUD5h6teB-480-80.jpg.webp 480w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/2qAsGfTHizMsQMUD5h6teB-650-80.jpg.webp 650w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/2qAsGfTHizMsQMUD5h6teB-970-80.jpg.webp 970w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/2qAsGfTHizMsQMUD5h6teB-1024-80.jpg.webp 1024w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/2qAsGfTHizMsQMUD5h6teB-1200-80.jpg.webp 1200w\" data-sizes=\"(min-width: 1000px) 970px, calc(100vw - 40px)\" data-original-mos=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/2qAsGfTHizMsQMUD5h6teB.jpg\" data-pin-media=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/2qAsGfTHizMsQMUD5h6teB.jpg\"></source><source type=\"image/jpeg\" alt=\"Assassin\'s Creed Codename Red\" class=\" lazy-image-van\" onerror=\"if(this.src &amp;&amp; this.src.indexOf(\'missing-image.svg\') !== -1){return true;};this.parentNode.replaceChild(window.missingImage(),this)\" data-normal=\"https://vanilla.futurecdn.net/gamesradar/media/img/missing-image.svg\" data-srcset=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/2qAsGfTHizMsQMUD5h6teB-320-80.jpg 320w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/2qAsGfTHizMsQMUD5h6teB-480-80.jpg 480w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/2qAsGfTHizMsQMUD5h6teB-650-80.jpg 650w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/2qAsGfTHizMsQMUD5h6teB-970-80.jpg 970w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/2qAsGfTHizMsQMUD5h6teB-1024-80.jpg 1024w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/2qAsGfTHizMsQMUD5h6teB-1200-80.jpg 1200w\" data-sizes=\"(min-width: 1000px) 970px, calc(100vw - 40px)\" data-original-mos=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/2qAsGfTHizMsQMUD5h6teB.jpg\" data-pin-media=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/2qAsGfTHizMsQMUD5h6teB.jpg\"></source><img src=\"https://vanilla.futurecdn.net/gamesradar/media/img/missing-image.svg\" alt=\"Assassin\'s Creed Codename Red\" class=\" lazy-image-van\" onerror=\"if(this.src &amp;&amp; this.src.indexOf(\'missing-image.svg\') !== -1){return true;};this.parentNode.replaceChild(window.missingImage(),this)\" data-normal=\"https://vanilla.futurecdn.net/gamesradar/media/img/missing-image.svg\" data-srcset=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/2qAsGfTHizMsQMUD5h6teB-320-80.jpg 320w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/2qAsGfTHizMsQMUD5h6teB-480-80.jpg 480w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/2qAsGfTHizMsQMUD5h6teB-650-80.jpg 650w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/2qAsGfTHizMsQMUD5h6teB-970-80.jpg 970w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/2qAsGfTHizMsQMUD5h6teB-1024-80.jpg 1024w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/2qAsGfTHizMsQMUD5h6teB-1200-80.jpg 1200w\" data-sizes=\"(min-width: 1000px) 970px, calc(100vw - 40px)\" data-original-mos=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/2qAsGfTHizMsQMUD5h6teB.jpg\" data-pin-media=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/2qAsGfTHizMsQMUD5h6teB.jpg\"></picture></p>\n<figcaption itemprop=\"caption description\" class=\" inline-layout\"><span class=\"credit\" itemprop=\"copyrightHolder\">(Image credit: Ubisoft)</span></figcaption></figure><p><strong>Developer:</strong> Ubisoft Quebec&#160;<br><strong>Platform(s):</strong> TBC<br><strong>Release Date:</strong> TBC</p>\n<p>Assassin\'s Creed Codename Red is expected to be the first game to join the Infinity Hub, and the sequel that will finally deliver on a longstanding fan-request: Codename Red is set in feudal Japan. In development at Assassin\'s Creed Odyssey\'s Ubisoft Quebec, Codename Red will let us live out a \"very powerful shinobi fantasy\" and has been described as the future of the open-world RPG Assassin\'s Creed games. It\'s a wildly exciting proposition, and we\'re eager to see what Ubisoft delivers here. As for a release date, a recent LinkedIn post from the Ubisoft office team hinted that Codename Red will be a 2024 blockbuster title...not long to wait now.</p>\n<h2 id=\"assassin-apos-s-creed-codename-hexe\">Assassin\'s Creed Codename Hexe</h2>\n<figure class=\"van-image-figure inline-layout\" data-bordeaux-image-check><p class=\"vanilla-image-block\" style=\"padding-top:56.25%;\"><picture><source type=\"image/webp\" alt=\"Assassin\'s Creed Codename Hexe screenshot\" class=\" lazy-image-van\" onerror=\"if(this.src &amp;&amp; this.src.indexOf(\'missing-image.svg\') !== -1){return true;};this.parentNode.replaceChild(window.missingImage(),this)\" data-normal=\"https://vanilla.futurecdn.net/gamesradar/media/img/missing-image.svg\" data-srcset=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/REH8wXqBMq42Qj7YLhSvxK-320-80.jpg.webp 320w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/REH8wXqBMq42Qj7YLhSvxK-480-80.jpg.webp 480w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/REH8wXqBMq42Qj7YLhSvxK-650-80.jpg.webp 650w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/REH8wXqBMq42Qj7YLhSvxK-970-80.jpg.webp 970w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/REH8wXqBMq42Qj7YLhSvxK-1024-80.jpg.webp 1024w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/REH8wXqBMq42Qj7YLhSvxK-1200-80.jpg.webp 1200w\" data-sizes=\"(min-width: 1000px) 970px, calc(100vw - 40px)\" data-original-mos=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/REH8wXqBMq42Qj7YLhSvxK.jpg\" data-pin-media=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/REH8wXqBMq42Qj7YLhSvxK.jpg\"></source><source type=\"image/jpeg\" alt=\"Assassin\'s Creed Codename Hexe screenshot\" class=\" lazy-image-van\" onerror=\"if(this.src &amp;&amp; this.src.indexOf(\'missing-image.svg\') !== -1){return true;};this.parentNode.replaceChild(window.missingImage(),this)\" data-normal=\"https://vanilla.futurecdn.net/gamesradar/media/img/missing-image.svg\" data-srcset=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/REH8wXqBMq42Qj7YLhSvxK-320-80.jpg 320w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/REH8wXqBMq42Qj7YLhSvxK-480-80.jpg 480w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/REH8wXqBMq42Qj7YLhSvxK-650-80.jpg 650w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/REH8wXqBMq42Qj7YLhSvxK-970-80.jpg 970w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/REH8wXqBMq42Qj7YLhSvxK-1024-80.jpg 1024w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/REH8wXqBMq42Qj7YLhSvxK-1200-80.jpg 1200w\" data-sizes=\"(min-width: 1000px) 970px, calc(100vw - 40px)\" data-original-mos=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/REH8wXqBMq42Qj7YLhSvxK.jpg\" data-pin-media=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/REH8wXqBMq42Qj7YLhSvxK.jpg\"></source><img src=\"https://vanilla.futurecdn.net/gamesradar/media/img/missing-image.svg\" alt=\"Assassin\'s Creed Codename Hexe screenshot\" class=\" lazy-image-van\" onerror=\"if(this.src &amp;&amp; this.src.indexOf(\'missing-image.svg\') !== -1){return true;};this.parentNode.replaceChild(window.missingImage(),this)\" data-normal=\"https://vanilla.futurecdn.net/gamesradar/media/img/missing-image.svg\" data-srcset=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/REH8wXqBMq42Qj7YLhSvxK-320-80.jpg 320w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/REH8wXqBMq42Qj7YLhSvxK-480-80.jpg 480w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/REH8wXqBMq42Qj7YLhSvxK-650-80.jpg 650w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/REH8wXqBMq42Qj7YLhSvxK-970-80.jpg 970w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/REH8wXqBMq42Qj7YLhSvxK-1024-80.jpg 1024w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/REH8wXqBMq42Qj7YLhSvxK-1200-80.jpg 1200w\" data-sizes=\"(min-width: 1000px) 970px, calc(100vw - 40px)\" data-original-mos=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/REH8wXqBMq42Qj7YLhSvxK.jpg\" data-pin-media=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/REH8wXqBMq42Qj7YLhSvxK.jpg\"></picture></p>\n<figcaption itemprop=\"caption description\" class=\" inline-layout\"><span class=\"credit\" itemprop=\"copyrightHolder\">(Image credit: Ubisoft)</span></figcaption></figure><p><strong>Developer:</strong> Ubisoft Montreal&#160;<br><strong>Platform(s):</strong> TBC<br><strong>Release Date:</strong> TBC</p>\n<p>Assassin\'s Creed Codename Hexe is being positioned as a \"a very different type of Assassins\' Creed game.\" Details are few and far between, but we do know that it\'s being created by Assassin\'s Creed Valhalla developer Ubisoft Montreal and that former Watch Dogs Legion creative director Clint Hocking will be leading production. The first teaser trailer and game\'s codename suggest that Assassin\'s Creed Hexe will be set in 16th Century Europe during the infamous witch trials that engulfed the region. We could be in for a weird, subversive open world RPG here with Codename Hexe, and we\'re honestly here for a little more experimentation from the Assassin\'s Creed series.&#160;</p>\n<h2 id=\"assassin-apos-s-creed-jade\">Assassin\'s Creed Jade</h2>\n<figure class=\"van-image-figure inline-layout\" data-bordeaux-image-check><p class=\"vanilla-image-block\" style=\"padding-top:56.25%;\"><picture><source type=\"image/webp\" alt=\"Assassin\'s Creed Jade\" class=\" lazy-image-van\" onerror=\"if(this.src &amp;&amp; this.src.indexOf(\'missing-image.svg\') !== -1){return true;};this.parentNode.replaceChild(window.missingImage(),this)\" data-normal=\"https://vanilla.futurecdn.net/gamesradar/media/img/missing-image.svg\" data-srcset=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/RSDqPoXjqfRbbKLdBXpdcS-320-80.jpg.webp 320w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/RSDqPoXjqfRbbKLdBXpdcS-480-80.jpg.webp 480w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/RSDqPoXjqfRbbKLdBXpdcS-650-80.jpg.webp 650w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/RSDqPoXjqfRbbKLdBXpdcS-970-80.jpg.webp 970w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/RSDqPoXjqfRbbKLdBXpdcS-1024-80.jpg.webp 1024w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/RSDqPoXjqfRbbKLdBXpdcS-1200-80.jpg.webp 1200w\" data-sizes=\"(min-width: 1000px) 970px, calc(100vw - 40px)\" data-original-mos=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/RSDqPoXjqfRbbKLdBXpdcS.jpg\" data-pin-media=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/RSDqPoXjqfRbbKLdBXpdcS.jpg\"></source><source type=\"image/jpeg\" alt=\"Assassin\'s Creed Jade\" class=\" lazy-image-van\" onerror=\"if(this.src &amp;&amp; this.src.indexOf(\'missing-image.svg\') !== -1){return true;};this.parentNode.replaceChild(window.missingImage(),this)\" data-normal=\"https://vanilla.futurecdn.net/gamesradar/media/img/missing-image.svg\" data-srcset=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/RSDqPoXjqfRbbKLdBXpdcS-320-80.jpg 320w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/RSDqPoXjqfRbbKLdBXpdcS-480-80.jpg 480w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/RSDqPoXjqfRbbKLdBXpdcS-650-80.jpg 650w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/RSDqPoXjqfRbbKLdBXpdcS-970-80.jpg 970w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/RSDqPoXjqfRbbKLdBXpdcS-1024-80.jpg 1024w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/RSDqPoXjqfRbbKLdBXpdcS-1200-80.jpg 1200w\" data-sizes=\"(min-width: 1000px) 970px, calc(100vw - 40px)\" data-original-mos=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/RSDqPoXjqfRbbKLdBXpdcS.jpg\" data-pin-media=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/RSDqPoXjqfRbbKLdBXpdcS.jpg\"></source><img src=\"https://vanilla.futurecdn.net/gamesradar/media/img/missing-image.svg\" alt=\"Assassin\'s Creed Jade\" class=\" lazy-image-van\" onerror=\"if(this.src &amp;&amp; this.src.indexOf(\'missing-image.svg\') !== -1){return true;};this.parentNode.replaceChild(window.missingImage(),this)\" data-normal=\"https://vanilla.futurecdn.net/gamesradar/media/img/missing-image.svg\" data-srcset=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/RSDqPoXjqfRbbKLdBXpdcS-320-80.jpg 320w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/RSDqPoXjqfRbbKLdBXpdcS-480-80.jpg 480w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/RSDqPoXjqfRbbKLdBXpdcS-650-80.jpg 650w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/RSDqPoXjqfRbbKLdBXpdcS-970-80.jpg 970w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/RSDqPoXjqfRbbKLdBXpdcS-1024-80.jpg 1024w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/RSDqPoXjqfRbbKLdBXpdcS-1200-80.jpg 1200w\" data-sizes=\"(min-width: 1000px) 970px, calc(100vw - 40px)\" data-original-mos=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/RSDqPoXjqfRbbKLdBXpdcS.jpg\" data-pin-media=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/RSDqPoXjqfRbbKLdBXpdcS.jpg\"></picture></p>\n<figcaption itemprop=\"caption description\" class=\" inline-layout\"><span class=\"credit\" itemprop=\"copyrightHolder\">(Image credit: Ubisoft)</span></figcaption></figure><p><strong>Developer:</strong> Ubisoft&#160;<br><strong>Platform(s):</strong> Android, iOS<br><strong>Release Date:</strong> TBC</p>\n<p>Assassin\'s Creed Jade is set to be the first truly open world Assassin\'s Creed game for mobile. Ubisoft has said that it\'s trying to build an authentic Assassin\'s Creed experience, albeit one that is totally optimized for touch controls. Assassin\'s Creed Jade will be set in China in the year 215 BCE &#8211; and, yes, you will be about to parkour across the Great Wall. Originally revealed as Codename Jade before it\'s official title was confirmed at GamesCom 2023 as simply Assassin\'s Creed Jade, it will also be the first game in the series to let you create your own assassin from scratch, which is a nice touch.&#160;</p>\n<h2 id=\"assassin-apos-s-creed-netflix\">Assassin\'s Creed Netflix</h2>\n<figure class=\"van-image-figure inline-layout\" data-bordeaux-image-check><p class=\"vanilla-image-block\" style=\"padding-top:56.25%;\"><picture><source type=\"image/webp\" alt=\"Assassin\'s Creed Netflix\" class=\" lazy-image-van\" onerror=\"if(this.src &amp;&amp; this.src.indexOf(\'missing-image.svg\') !== -1){return true;};this.parentNode.replaceChild(window.missingImage(),this)\" data-normal=\"https://vanilla.futurecdn.net/gamesradar/media/img/missing-image.svg\" data-srcset=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/pkoEWdqioJ2cSMSD8vzSAg-320-80.jpg.webp 320w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/pkoEWdqioJ2cSMSD8vzSAg-480-80.jpg.webp 480w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/pkoEWdqioJ2cSMSD8vzSAg-650-80.jpg.webp 650w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/pkoEWdqioJ2cSMSD8vzSAg-970-80.jpg.webp 970w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/pkoEWdqioJ2cSMSD8vzSAg-1024-80.jpg.webp 1024w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/pkoEWdqioJ2cSMSD8vzSAg-1200-80.jpg.webp 1200w\" data-sizes=\"(min-width: 1000px) 970px, calc(100vw - 40px)\" data-original-mos=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/pkoEWdqioJ2cSMSD8vzSAg.jpg\" data-pin-media=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/pkoEWdqioJ2cSMSD8vzSAg.jpg\"></source><source type=\"image/jpeg\" alt=\"Assassin\'s Creed Netflix\" class=\" lazy-image-van\" onerror=\"if(this.src &amp;&amp; this.src.indexOf(\'missing-image.svg\') !== -1){return true;};this.parentNode.replaceChild(window.missingImage(),this)\" data-normal=\"https://vanilla.futurecdn.net/gamesradar/media/img/missing-image.svg\" data-srcset=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/pkoEWdqioJ2cSMSD8vzSAg-320-80.jpg 320w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/pkoEWdqioJ2cSMSD8vzSAg-480-80.jpg 480w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/pkoEWdqioJ2cSMSD8vzSAg-650-80.jpg 650w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/pkoEWdqioJ2cSMSD8vzSAg-970-80.jpg 970w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/pkoEWdqioJ2cSMSD8vzSAg-1024-80.jpg 1024w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/pkoEWdqioJ2cSMSD8vzSAg-1200-80.jpg 1200w\" data-sizes=\"(min-width: 1000px) 970px, calc(100vw - 40px)\" data-original-mos=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/pkoEWdqioJ2cSMSD8vzSAg.jpg\" data-pin-media=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/pkoEWdqioJ2cSMSD8vzSAg.jpg\"></source><img src=\"https://vanilla.futurecdn.net/gamesradar/media/img/missing-image.svg\" alt=\"Assassin\'s Creed Netflix\" class=\" lazy-image-van\" onerror=\"if(this.src &amp;&amp; this.src.indexOf(\'missing-image.svg\') !== -1){return true;};this.parentNode.replaceChild(window.missingImage(),this)\" data-normal=\"https://vanilla.futurecdn.net/gamesradar/media/img/missing-image.svg\" data-srcset=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/pkoEWdqioJ2cSMSD8vzSAg-320-80.jpg 320w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/pkoEWdqioJ2cSMSD8vzSAg-480-80.jpg 480w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/pkoEWdqioJ2cSMSD8vzSAg-650-80.jpg 650w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/pkoEWdqioJ2cSMSD8vzSAg-970-80.jpg 970w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/pkoEWdqioJ2cSMSD8vzSAg-1024-80.jpg 1024w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/pkoEWdqioJ2cSMSD8vzSAg-1200-80.jpg 1200w\" data-sizes=\"(min-width: 1000px) 970px, calc(100vw - 40px)\" data-original-mos=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/pkoEWdqioJ2cSMSD8vzSAg.jpg\" data-pin-media=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/pkoEWdqioJ2cSMSD8vzSAg.jpg\"></picture></p>\n<figcaption itemprop=\"caption description\" class=\" inline-layout\"><span class=\"credit\" itemprop=\"copyrightHolder\">(Image credit: Ubisoft)</span></figcaption></figure><p><strong>Developer:</strong> Ubisoft&#160;<br><strong>Platform(s):</strong> Android, iOS<br><strong>Release Date:</strong> TBC</p>\n<p>Ubisoft and Netflix have entered a pretty broad collaboration agreement. There\'s a Netflix Assassin\'s Creed series in production (with showrunner Jed Stuart at the helm; the writer of such iconic action movies as Die Hard and The Fugitive), and <em>three</em> mobile games in development for Netflix\'s video game platform. There are games based on the Valiant Hearts and Mighty Quest universes coming, and of course one based in the world of Assassin\'s Creed too. The Assassin\'s Creed Netflix game is in early development, but when it does launch it\'ll be available exclusively on mobile to Netflix subscribers around the world. No other information was shared, but our curiosity has been piqued all the same.&#160;</p>\n<h2 id=\"assassin-apos-s-creed-invictus\">Assassin\'s Creed Invictus</h2>\n<figure class=\"van-image-figure inline-layout\" data-bordeaux-image-check><p class=\"vanilla-image-block\" style=\"padding-top:56.25%;\"><picture><source type=\"image/webp\" alt=\"Assassin\'s Creed Infinity roadmap\" class=\" lazy-image-van\" onerror=\"if(this.src &amp;&amp; this.src.indexOf(\'missing-image.svg\') !== -1){return true;};this.parentNode.replaceChild(window.missingImage(),this)\" data-normal=\"https://vanilla.futurecdn.net/gamesradar/media/img/missing-image.svg\" data-srcset=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/wVSBSxWQ9YPaKGHa3FjprY-320-80.jpg.webp 320w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/wVSBSxWQ9YPaKGHa3FjprY-480-80.jpg.webp 480w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/wVSBSxWQ9YPaKGHa3FjprY-650-80.jpg.webp 650w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/wVSBSxWQ9YPaKGHa3FjprY-970-80.jpg.webp 970w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/wVSBSxWQ9YPaKGHa3FjprY-1024-80.jpg.webp 1024w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/wVSBSxWQ9YPaKGHa3FjprY-1200-80.jpg.webp 1200w\" data-sizes=\"(min-width: 1000px) 970px, calc(100vw - 40px)\" data-original-mos=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/wVSBSxWQ9YPaKGHa3FjprY.jpg\" data-pin-media=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/wVSBSxWQ9YPaKGHa3FjprY.jpg\"></source><source type=\"image/jpeg\" alt=\"Assassin\'s Creed Infinity roadmap\" class=\" lazy-image-van\" onerror=\"if(this.src &amp;&amp; this.src.indexOf(\'missing-image.svg\') !== -1){return true;};this.parentNode.replaceChild(window.missingImage(),this)\" data-normal=\"https://vanilla.futurecdn.net/gamesradar/media/img/missing-image.svg\" data-srcset=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/wVSBSxWQ9YPaKGHa3FjprY-320-80.jpg 320w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/wVSBSxWQ9YPaKGHa3FjprY-480-80.jpg 480w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/wVSBSxWQ9YPaKGHa3FjprY-650-80.jpg 650w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/wVSBSxWQ9YPaKGHa3FjprY-970-80.jpg 970w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/wVSBSxWQ9YPaKGHa3FjprY-1024-80.jpg 1024w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/wVSBSxWQ9YPaKGHa3FjprY-1200-80.jpg 1200w\" data-sizes=\"(min-width: 1000px) 970px, calc(100vw - 40px)\" data-original-mos=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/wVSBSxWQ9YPaKGHa3FjprY.jpg\" data-pin-media=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/wVSBSxWQ9YPaKGHa3FjprY.jpg\"></source><img src=\"https://vanilla.futurecdn.net/gamesradar/media/img/missing-image.svg\" alt=\"Assassin\'s Creed Infinity roadmap\" class=\" lazy-image-van\" onerror=\"if(this.src &amp;&amp; this.src.indexOf(\'missing-image.svg\') !== -1){return true;};this.parentNode.replaceChild(window.missingImage(),this)\" data-normal=\"https://vanilla.futurecdn.net/gamesradar/media/img/missing-image.svg\" data-srcset=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/wVSBSxWQ9YPaKGHa3FjprY-320-80.jpg 320w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/wVSBSxWQ9YPaKGHa3FjprY-480-80.jpg 480w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/wVSBSxWQ9YPaKGHa3FjprY-650-80.jpg 650w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/wVSBSxWQ9YPaKGHa3FjprY-970-80.jpg 970w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/wVSBSxWQ9YPaKGHa3FjprY-1024-80.jpg 1024w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/wVSBSxWQ9YPaKGHa3FjprY-1200-80.jpg 1200w\" data-sizes=\"(min-width: 1000px) 970px, calc(100vw - 40px)\" data-original-mos=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/wVSBSxWQ9YPaKGHa3FjprY.jpg\" data-pin-media=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/wVSBSxWQ9YPaKGHa3FjprY.jpg\"></picture></p>\n<figcaption itemprop=\"caption description\" class=\" inline-layout\"><span class=\"credit\" itemprop=\"copyrightHolder\">(Image credit: Ubisoft)</span></figcaption></figure><p><strong>Developer:</strong> Ubisoft&#160; <br><strong>Platform(s):</strong> TBC<br><strong>Release Date:</strong> TBC</p>\n<p>Ubisoft says that it is \"investigating how we will bring back standalone multiplayer experiences into the Assassin\'s Creed universe.\" Assassin\'s Creed multiplayer has been atop wish-lists for years now &#8211; it\'s been nine years since the mode featured in AC4: Black Flag, and eight since co-op appeared in Assassin\'s Creed Unity. Little is known about this standalone Assassin\'s Creed multiplayer game, although we know that it\'ll launch as part of the Assassin\'s Creed Infinity Hub, and franchise boss Marc-Alexis Cot&#233; has confirmed that the codename is \'Assassin\'s Creed Invictus\'.</p>\n<p><em>Return to one of the </em><em>best Assassin\'s Creed games</em><em> while you wait these out.</em></p>', '2024-03-11 11:51:14', '2024-03-11 11:51:14', 'Upcoming Assassin\'s Creed games: Every new Assassin\'s Creed game in development', 'https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/RbRXW98GZLTsJX9wwqFmSA.jpg', 'games', 'https://www.gamesradar.com/upcoming-assassins-creed-games/', 'There are so many upcoming Assassin\'s Creed games in the works. From an interest...', '');
INSERT INTO `ch_gather` (`id`, `user_id`, `content`, `create_time`, `update_time`, `title`, `image`, `type`, `url`, `introduction`, `column`) VALUES
(234, NULL, '<p>Mario Day is nigh! This weekend we\'ll see the return of one of the most hallowed days in Ninty\'s calendar; March 10 (it\'s MAR10 - geddit). Retailers generally take this opportunity to serve up a whole load of Nintendo Switch deals and 2024 is looking no different.&#160;</p>\n\n<p>We\'ve got up to $20 off some of Mario\'s biggest games as well as record low prices on accessories as well. If you\'re yet to dive in, it\'s worth noting we\'re also seeing some of the best Nintendo Switch bundles of the year on the shelves right now as well. These are package deals that we generally only ever see during Black Friday\'s offerings - but they\'ve made their way back to the shelves for this year\'s Mario Day deals.&#160;</p>\n<p>Top picks include the Nintendo Switch standard console with Mario Kart 8 Deluxe and three months of the Online subscription for <strong>$299 at Amazon</strong>, Super Mario RPG dropping all the way down to <strong>$44.95 (was $59.99) at Walmart</strong>, and one of our favorite cases, the TomToc Slim, sitting at just <strong>$19.99 at Amazon</strong> as well.&#160;</p>\n<p>You\'ll find all our top picks from this weekend\'s Mario Day sales just below.&#160;</p>\n<h2 id=\"today-apos-s-best-mario-day-deals\">Today\'s best Mario Day deals</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<strong>Amazon: </strong>free Mario Kart 8 with console\n</li>\n<li>\n<strong>Best Buy: </strong>up to $20 off Mario games\n</li>\n<li>\n<strong>GameStop: </strong>up to 30% off digital titles\n</li>\n<li>\n<strong>Walmart: </strong>save on Mario Lego and more\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 class=\"article-body__section\" id=\"section-best-mario-day-console-deals\"><span>Best Mario Day console deals</span></h2>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/mtpcPUSFSt2aW4NMpHCFnE-200-100.jpg\" alt=\"Nintendo Switch Lite | Animal Crossing: New Horizons | $199 at Walmart\" title=\"Nintendo Switch Lite | Animal Crossing: New Horizons | $199 at Walmart\" class=\"hawk-lazy-image-deal-widget\" draggable=\"false\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"140\" height=\"160\">\n\n<p><strong>Nintendo Switch Lite | Animal Crossing: New Horizons | </strong><strong>$199 at Walmart</strong><strong><br></strong>Walmart still has this Animal Crossing: New Horizons bundle on the shelves, packing both the handheld console and a free copy of your next island adventure.&#160;</p>\n<p><strong>Buy it if:&#160;</strong></p>\n<p><strong>&#9989; </strong>You don\'t want to play in docked mode<br><strong>&#9989; </strong>You want to spend as little as possible<br><strong>&#9989; </strong>You\'re buying for younger players</p>\n<p><strong>Don\'t buy it if:&#160;</strong></p>\n<p>&#10060; You\'re prioritizing screen quality<br>\n&#10060; You want to play on the TV</p>\n<p><strong>Price Check: </strong>Amazon: $197.98 (no game) | Best Buy: $199.99 (no game)<br></p>\n\n\n<span>View Deal</span>\n\n\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/veMNTdztohFMgeyhkEwz7L-200-100.jpg\" alt=\"Nintendo Switch | Mario Kart 8 Deluxe | 3 months Nintendo Switch Online | $299 at Amazon\" title=\"Nintendo Switch | Mario Kart 8 Deluxe | 3 months Nintendo Switch Online | $299 at Amazon\" class=\"hawk-lazy-image-deal-widget\" draggable=\"false\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"140\" height=\"160\">\n\n<p><strong>Nintendo Switch | Mario Kart 8 Deluxe | 3 months Nintendo Switch Online | </strong><strong>$299 at Amazon</strong><strong><br></strong>We generally only see this Nintendo Switch bundle over Black Friday, but it\'s back on the shelves at Amazon just in time for Mario Day. You\'re getting the standard edition console here, as well as a free copy of Mario Kart 8 Deluxe and three months of Nintendo Switch Online to boo.</p>\n<p><strong>Buy it if:&#160;</strong></p>\n<p>&#9989; You will mostly play in docked mode<br>\n&#9989; You\'re a karting fan <br>\n&#9989; You don\'t mind the LCD panel</p>\n<p><strong>Don\'t buy it if:&#160;</strong></p>\n<p>&#10060; You\'ll mostly play handheld mode</p>\n<p><strong>Price Check: </strong>Walmart: $357.95 | <del>Best Buy: OOS</del><br></p>\n\n\n<span>View Deal</span>\n\n\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/AkL4XJwNaxTd4xbf26jPHV-200-100.jpg\" alt=\"Nintendo Switch OLED | Mario Kart 8 Deluxe | $349.99 at Walmart\" title=\"Nintendo Switch OLED | Mario Kart 8 Deluxe | $349.99 at Walmart\" class=\"hawk-lazy-image-deal-widget\" draggable=\"false\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"140\" height=\"160\">\n\n<p><strong>Nintendo Switch OLED | Mario Kart 8 Deluxe | </strong><strong>$349.99 at Walmart</strong><strong><br></strong>Walmart has its own take on the Mario Kart 8 bundle, with the OLED model stepping up to the plate. We saw a similar offer at the end of last year with three months of Nintendo Switch Online thrown in as well - but this is just the console and free game.&#160;</p>\n<p><strong>Buy it if:&#160;</strong></p>\n<p>&#9989; You mostly play in handheld mode...<br>\n&#9989; ... but still want the option to dock<br>\n&#9989; You prioritize screen quality</p>\n<p><strong>Don\'t buy it if:&#160;</strong></p>\n<p>&#10060; You only play in docked mode</p>\n<p><strong>Price Check: </strong>Amazon: $339 (no game) | Best Buy: $349.99 (no game)<br></p>\n\n\n<span>View Deal</span>\n\n<h2 class=\"article-body__section\" id=\"section-best-mario-day-games-deals\"><span>Best Mario Day games deals</span></h2>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/aR4YWpw7ryUvZJpu3brfVF-200-100.jpg\" alt=\"Mario Kart 8 Deluxe (Digital) | $59.99 $39.99 at Amazon\nSave $20 -\" title=\"Mario Kart 8 Deluxe (Digital) | $59.99 $39.99 at Amazon\nSave $20 -\" class=\"hawk-lazy-image-deal-widget\" draggable=\"false\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"140\" height=\"160\">\n\n<p><strong>Mario Kart 8 Deluxe (Digital) | </strong><del>$59.99</del><strong> $39.99 at Amazon</strong><strong><br></strong><em><strong>Save $20 - </strong></em>Mario Kart 8 Deluxe might have been a launch day hit, but it still regularly sits at its regular $59.99 MSRP. This is about as cheap as the 