options to the next level, Mario Party Superstars is going to go down a storm. We have seen this digital edition $10 cheaper in the past - but that was only once and very briefly back in 2022.&#160;</p>\n<p><strong>Buy it if:&#160;</strong></p>\n<p>&#9989; You like multiplayer minigames<br>\n&#9989; You\'re a fan of the series&#160;</p>\n<p><strong>Don\'t buy it if:&#160;</strong></p>\n<p>&#10060; You\'re a solo player</p>\n<p><strong>Price Check: </strong>Walmart: $39.99 | Best Buy: $59.99<br></p>\n\n\n<span>View Deal</span>\n\n\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/ZJLcRHPtSrnABC5QSAjufU-200-100.jpg\" alt=\"Super Mario RPG | $59.99 $44.95 at Walmart\nSave $15 -\" title=\"Super Mario RPG | $59.99 $44.95 at Walmart\nSave $15 -\" class=\"hawk-lazy-image-deal-widget\" draggable=\"false\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"140\" height=\"160\">\n\n<p><strong>Super Mario RPG | </strong><del>$59.99</del><strong> $44.95 at Walmart</strong><strong><br></strong><em><strong>Save $15 - </strong></em>Walmart has the best price on Super Mario RPG for Mario Day this weekend, dropping the newer release down to just $44.95. That\'s pretty much the best price we\'ve ever seen on this one.&#160;</p>\n<p><strong>Buy it if:&#160;</strong></p>\n<p>&#9989; You enjoyed the original<br>\n&#9989; You like turn based combat<br>\n&#9989; You want something different from Mario&#160;</p>\n<p><strong>Don\'t buy it if:&#160;</strong></p>\n<p>&#10060; You\'re after classic Mario platforming&#160;</p>\n<p><strong>Price Check: </strong>Amazon: $49.49 | Best Buy: $59.99</p>\n\n\n<span>View Deal</span>\n\n\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/XRQw8Y3xScs7D8zgG79n84-200-100.jpg\" alt=\"Super Mario Bros. Wonder | $59.99 $48.26 at Walmart\nSave $11 -\" title=\"Super Mario Bros. Wonder | $59.99 $48.26 at Walmart\nSave $11 -\" class=\"hawk-lazy-image-deal-widget\" draggable=\"false\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"140\" height=\"160\">\n\n<p><strong>Super Mario Bros. Wonder | </strong><del>$59.99</d